%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hyderabad%20Man%20Allegedly%20Forced%20to%20Join%20Russian%20Army%20Dies%20in%20Ukraine%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F13144455%2FSouth_Ossetia_war_58_army.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%2030-year-old%20man%20from%20Hyderabad%2C%20who%20was%20allegedly%20forced%20to%20join%20the%20Russian%20Army%20after%20falling%20prey%20to%20a%20job%20fraud%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20ongoing%20war%20with%20Ukraine%2C%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fhyderabad-man-mohammed-asfan-dies-fighting-russia-allegedly-duped-joining-war-2511350-2024-03-06%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20officials%2C%20on%20Wednesday%20(March%206).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20of%20the%20man%2C%20identified%20as%20Mohammed%20Asfan%2C%20reached%20out%20to%20All%20India%20Majlis-E-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20chief%20and%20Hyderabad%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20seeking%20assistance%20in%20bringing%20him%20back%20from%20Russia.%20However%2C%20when%20AIMIM%20contacted%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Moscow%2C%20officials%20confirmed%20that%20Asfan%20had%20died%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20report%2C%20Embassy%20of%20India%20in%20Russia%20has%20tweeted%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20learnt%20about%20the%20tragic%20death%20of%20an%20Indian%20national%20Mohammed%20Asfan.%20We%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20family%20and%20Russian%20authorities.%20Mission%20will%20make%20efforts%20to%20send%20his%20mortal%20remains%20to%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWe%20have%20learnt%20about%20the%20tragic%20death%20of%20an%20Indian%20national%20Shri%20Mohammed%20Asfan.%20We%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20family%20and%20Russian%20authorities.%20Mission%20will%20make%20efforts%20to%20send%20his%20mortal%20remains%20to%20India.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMEAIndia%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40MEAIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20India%20in%20Russia%20(%40IndEmbMoscow)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndEmbMoscow%2Fstatus%2F1765371546074329434%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%206%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsfan%2C%20along%20with%20several%20others%2C%20allegedly%20fell%20victim%20to%20deceptive%20agents%20who%20recruited%20them%20as%20%E2%80%98helpers%E2%80%99%20to%20aid%20the%20Russian%20Army%20in%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20news%20comes%20weeks%20after%20a%2023-year-old%20Indian%20man%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHamil%20Mangukiya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20died%20in%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fgujarati-security-helper-in-russian-army-killed-in-ukrainian-air-strike%2Farticle67882488.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20was%20hired%20as%20a%20security%20helper%20by%20the%20Russian%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fhyderabad-man-mohammed-asfan-dies-fighting-russia-allegedly-duped-joining-war-2511350-2024-03-06%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Mangukiya%20had%20applied%20for%20a%20job%20in%20Russia%20through%20an%20online%20advertisement%20and%20reached%20Moscow%20from%20Chennai.%20He%20was%20killed%20in%20an%20airstrike%20by%20Ukraine%20on%20February%2021%20in%20the%20Donetsk%20region%20of%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2029%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%2C%20during%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20said%20that%20there%20are%20%E2%80%9C20-odd%20people%20(Indians)%20who%20have%20gone%20their%20to%20work%20as%20support%20staff%20or%20as%20helpers%20with%20the%20Russian%20army.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20trying%20our%20level%20best%20for%20their%20early%20discharge%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmea-reiterates-it-is-pursuing-discharge-of-indians-lured-into-russian-army-as-more-reports-emerge%5C%22%3Eas%20per%20previous%20media%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20100%20Indians%20may%20have%20been%20recruited%20as%20security%20helpers%20by%20the%20Russian%20army.%20While%20they%20were%20assured%20that%20they%20would%20not%20be%20deployed%20in%20active%20conflict%20zones%2C%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20go%20to%20combat%20areas%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20frontline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20seven%20Indians%20who%20are%20stuck%20in%20Russia%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fthis-could-be-our-last-video-theyre-sending-us-to-war-zone-indians-stuck-in-russia-to-govt%5C%22%3Ereached%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20facilitate%20their%20discharge%20as%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20join%20the%20Russian%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%2C%20one%20of%20them%20said%20that%20they%20went%20to%20Russia%20on%20tourist%20visas%20and%20were%20detained%20by%20the%20police%20for%20not%20having%20a%20%E2%80%9Cslip%E2%80%9D.%20Subsequently%2C%20they%20were%20forced%20by%20the%20police%20to%20join%20the%20army%20as%20%E2%80%9Chelpers%E2%80%9D%20or%20risk%20facing%20a%2010-year%20jail%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20told%20that%20we%20only%20have%20to%20work%20as%20helpers.%20But%20they%20enlisted%20us%20for%20training%20in%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20and%20are%20preparing%20to%20send%20us%20to%20Ukraine.%20They%20kept%20us%20hungry%20and%20snatched%20our%20phones%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fthis-could-be-our-last-video-help-us-get-back-to-india-say-another-group-of-indians-forced-to-fight-in-russia%2Farticle67918412.ece%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20one%20of%20the%20men%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709734332000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2F13144455%2FSouth_Ossetia_war_58_army.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhyderabad-man-allegedly-forced-to-join-russian-army-dies-in-ukraine-war%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Following%20the%20report%2C%20Embassy%20of%20India%20in%20Russia%20has%20tweeted%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20learnt%20about%20the%20tragic%20death%20of%20an%20Indian%20national%20Mohammed%20Asfan.%20We%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20family%20and%20Russian%20authorities.%20Mission%20will%20make%20efforts%20to%20send%20his%20mortal%20remains%20to%20India.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhyderabad-man-allegedly-forced-to-join-russian-army-dies-in-ukraine-war%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20Call%3A%20Unions%20Claim%20Farmers%20Being%20Stopped%20From%20Marching%20to%20Delhi%20in%20Many%20States%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15202856%2Fimage-1831.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20unions%20leading%20the%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20protest%20since%20February%2013%20claimed%20that%20farmers%20from%20several%20states%20were%20being%20stopped%20from%20marching%20to%20Delhi%20in%20response%20to%20their%20call%20to%20reach%20Delhi%20by%20road%20and%20trains%20starting%20Wednesday%20(March%206).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ESince%20farmers%20from%20Punjab%20are%20currently%20stuck%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20due%20to%20excessive%20police%20force%2C%20farmers%20from%20other%20states%20were%20asked%20to%20reach%20Delhi%20by%20any%20means%20possible%20to%20mount%20pressure%20on%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20Union%20government%20regarding%20their%20key%20demands%2C%20including%20legally%20guaranteed%20minimum%20support%20prices%20(MSP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ESarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%2C%20convener%20of%20the%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%2C%20which%20is%20leading%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20protest%20along%20with%20splinter%20groups%20of%20the%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(which%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%202020-21%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest)%2C%20told%20the%20media%20that%20as%20many%20as%20130%20farmers%20were%20detained%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20including%2030%20at%20the%20Sawai%20Madhopur%20railway%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20unable%20to%20contact%20farmers%20coming%20from%20other%20parts%20of%20India%20%5Bincluding%5D%20Bihar%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20as%20well%20as%20southern%20states.%20But%20we%20apprehend%20that%20they%20%E2%80%A6%20may%20have%20been%20detained%20in%20these%20states%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Pandher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EMany%20states%20that%20Pandher%20mentioned%20are%20BJP-ruled%20states%20which%2C%20according%20to%20Pandher%2C%20have%20increased%20surveillance%20on%20farmers%20marching%20towards%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EPandher%20also%20said%20that%20security%20has%20also%20been%20heightened%20inside%20Delhi%2C%20including%20at%20railway%20and%20bus%20stations%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Jantar%20Mantar%20site%20where%20farmers%20were%20supposed%20to%20gather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20get%20to%20know%20the%20exact%20situation%20in%20couple%20of%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandher%20said%20while%20targeting%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20using%20all%20means%20possible%20to%20end%20their%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EHe%20said%20that%20despite%20pressure%2C%20their%20call%20for%20the%20march%20to%20Delhi%20would%20remain%20as%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20not%20return%20unless%20farmers%20get%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20to%20MSP%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandher%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESKM%E2%80%99s%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Mahapanchayat%20on%20March%2014%20in%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20SKM%2C%20which%20is%20not%20officially%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20Delhi%20Chalo%20call%2C%20has%20been%20gearing%20up%20for%20its%20%E2%80%98Kisan%20Mazdoor%20%3Cem%3EMahapanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(Hindi%20for%20%E2%80%98great%20council%20of%20farm%20labourers%E2%80%99)%20on%20March%2014%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20the%20SKM%2C%20the%20upcoming%20mahapanchayat%20will%20focus%20on%20all%20pending%20promises%20the%20BJP%20government%20made%20while%20taking%20back%20the%20three%20controversial%20farm%20laws%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20promises%20included%20fixing%20MSPs%20based%20on%20a%20formula%20that%20returns%20to%20a%20farmer%20the%20cost%20of%20producing%20a%20crop%20as%20well%20as%20a%20profit%20equalling%2050%25%20that%20amount%2C%20along%20with%20guaranteed%20procurement%2C%20which%20the%20SKM%20claimed%20was%20also%20promised%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%202014%20manifesto%20and%20originally%20recommended%20by%20the%20National%20Farmers%20Commission%20chaired%20by%20M.S.%20Swaminathan%20in%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ESKM%20member%20Darshan%20Pal%20said%20that%20the%20main%20debate%20on%20MSP%20is%20all%20about%20increasing%20the%20income%20of%20farmers%20and%20then%20rejuvenating%20the%20market%20through%20higher%20farmer%20growth%2C%20but%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20denying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20coming%20mahapanchayat%20where%20farmers%20would%20gather%20from%20across%20the%20country%20will%20help%20raising%20the%20issue%20and%20make%20it%20the%20centre-point%20of%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EOn%20whether%20the%20SKM%20will%20be%20allowed%20permission%20for%20the%20mahapanchayat%2C%20he%20said%20that%20while%20they%20have%20already%20applied%20for%20permission%20with%20the%20Delhi%20government%20as%20well%20as%20the%20home%20affairs%20ministry%2C%20he%20personally%20believed%20that%20the%20ministry%20may%20deny%20it%20permission%20given%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strong%20resistance%20to%20public%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ll%20get%20to%20know%20the%20exact%20status%20in%20couple%20of%20days.%20In%20case%20we%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20hold%20a%20mahapanchyat%20in%20Delhi%2C%20we%20will%20take%20a%20fresh%20call%20and%20decide%20a%20future%20course%20of%20action%20through%20a%20meeting%20before%20March%2014%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20SKM%20has%20also%20strongly%20protested%20and%20condemned%20the%20BJP%20for%20fielding%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Teni%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Kheri%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3ETeni%20is%20the%20father%20of%20Ashish%20Mishra%20Teni%2C%20who%20is%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20a%202021%20incident%20where%20he%20along%20with%20others%20allegedly%20mowed%20to%20death%20four%20farmers%20protesting%20in%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3EThe%20SKM%20has%20also%20called%20the%20senior%20Teni%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Ffarmers-workers-to-mark-black-day-on-tuesday-to-seek-ajay-mishra-tenis-dismissal-over-lakhimpur-kheri-ki