20the%20seat%2C%20represented%20earlier%20by%20his%20uncle%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%2C%20father%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20and%20later%2C%20his%20mother%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20bought%20a%20house%20there%20last%20month%2C%20signalling%20long-term%20plans%20for%20the%20Congress%20bastion%20that%20never%20a%20home%20for%20the%20Gandhis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20%26quot%3BGriha%20Pravesh%26quot%3B%20ceremony%2C%20held%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20February%2C%20vied%20for%20attention%20with%20the%20yatra.%20On%20February%2019%2C%20as%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20entered%20Amethi%2C%20Ms%20Irani%20held%20her%20public%20outreach%20programme%2C%20the%20Jan%20Samvad%20Vikas%20Yatra.%20Their%20paths%20did%20not%20cross.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Irani%20had%20set%20her%20cap%20for%20Amethi%20ahead%20of%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20That%20time%2C%20she%20had%20camped%20out%20in%20the%20constituency%20--%20held%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20for%20three%20consecutive%20terms%20--%20for%20days%20but%20lost%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20sever%20connections.%20Instead%2C%20she%20redoubled%20her%20efforts%20to%20please%20the%20people%2C%20coming%20and%20going%20there%20regularly%2C%20distributing%20gifts%20at%20festivals.%20Her%20party%20even%20declared%20Mr%20Gandhi%20%26quot%3Bmissing%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20constituency%20during%20one%20of%20his%20absences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20her%20efforts%20paid%20off.%20Amethi%20sent%20her%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20with%2055%2C000%20votes%20more%20than%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20now%20represents%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%20in%20parliament's%20lower%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20Smriti%20Irani%20has%20tossed%C2%A0%20a%20dare%20at%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20saying%20he%20should%20contest%20only%20from%20Amethi%20if%20he%20was%20so%20confident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20is%20confident%2C%20then%20without%2