20UPI%20(Unified%20Payments%20Interface)%2C%20many%20founders%20and%20tech%20pundits%20asked%20for%20the%20government%20to%20build%20and%20run%20an%20app%20store%20as%20a%20DPI.%20As%20someone%20who%20has%20been%20building%20DPIs%20for%20the%20last%20eight%20years%2C%20I%20am%20both%20fascinated%20and%20terrified%20by%20where%20this%20debate%20is%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20controversy%20lies%20a%20fundamental%20question%3A%20Should%20Google%2C%20which%20invested%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20to%20grow%20the%20Android%20ecosystem%2C%20be%20allowed%20to%20reap%20benefits%20of%20those%20investments%20by%20controlling%20the%20main%20distribution%20mechanism%20of%20apps%20in%20the%20Android%20ecosystem%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECalls%20For%20Intervention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20Play%20Store%20rules%20mandate%20that%20apps%20generating%20revenue%20through%20the%20store%20must%20use%20the%20company's%20own%20billing%20system%2C%20for%20which%20it%20charges%20a%20steep%20commission%20of%20up%20to%2030%25.%20This%20has%20drawn%20ire%20from%20many%20app%20makers%2C%20who%20argue%20that%20this%20policy%20not%20only%20forces%20them%20to%20pay%20exorbitant%20fees%20but%20also%20stifles%20innovation%20by%20preventing%20them%20from%20exploring%20alternative%20payment%20options%20that%20could%20be%20more%20cost-effective%20or%20better%20suited%20to%20their%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20defiance%20of%20these%20rules%2C%20some%20Indian%20app%20developers%20have%20attempted%20to%20circumvent%20Google's%20payment%20system%2C%20resulting%20in%20their%20apps%20being%20unceremoniously%20booted%20from%20the%20Play%20store.%20This%20heavy-handed%20approach%20has%20sparked%20calls%20for%20regulatory%20intervention%2C%20with%20demands%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20government-backed%20app%20store%20or%20a%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%20to%20counterbalance%20Google's%20dominance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20that%20some%20of%20you%20may%20have%2C%20is%20why%20can't%20someone%20else%20make%20or%20run%20an%20app%20store%3F%20Technically%2C%20Google%20even%20allows%20it%2C%20and%20in%20a%20recent%20ambitious%20move%2C%20PhonePe%20even%20launched%20their%20own%20Indus%20App%20Store.%20But%20you%20will%20see%20the%20issue%20when%20you%20go%20to%20their%20website%20and%20look%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bsteps%20to%20install%26quot%3B%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20We%20Prepared%20Enough%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20functions%20that%20an%20app-store%20performs%20is%20reviewing%20apps%20and%20making%20sure%20they%20are%20safe%20for%20consumers%20to%20use%20-%20that%20these%20apps%20are%20not%20stealing%20your%20identity%2C%20your%20data%2C%20or%20your%20money.%20You%20can%20theoretically%20download%20apps%20from%20outside%20of%20an%20app%20store%20by%20directly%20downloading%20them%2C%20but%20this%20is%20exactly%20what%20a%20scammer%20or%20malicious%20hacker%20would%20want%20you%20to%20do.%20Hence%2C%20the%20android%20ecosystem%20makes%20it%20hard%20(and%20scary)%20for%20you%20to%20download%20apps%20outside%20the%20app%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20allure%20of%20a%20state-run%20app%20store%20may%20seem%20tempting%20at%20first%20glance%2C%20one%20has%20to%20ask%20if%20we%20are%20actually%20prepared%20to%20build%20and%20run%20a%20parallel%20infrastructure%20that%20does%20all%20of%20these%20functions.%20There's%20the%20user%20experience%20of%20the%20app%20store%2C%20the%20manual%20reviewing%20and%20security%20testing%2C%20the%20hosting%2C%20storage%20and%20network%20costs%20of%20serving%20millions%20of%20app%20downloads%20every%20day%2C%20and%20the%20discretion%20that%20these%20app%20stores%20have%20on%20who%20gets%20visibility%20and%20who%20ranks%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENeed%20For%20Balance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20a%20more%20nuanced%20approach%20is%20needed%20-%20one%20that%20strikes%20a%20balance%20between%20fostering%20a%20healthy%20competitive%20landscape%20and%20preserving%20the%20incentives%20for%20continued%20investment%20and%20innovation.%20Rather%20than%20a%20full-fledged%20state-run%20app%20store%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bsurgical%20strike%26quot%3B%20DPI%20that%20empowers%20India%20to%20define%20its%20own%20standards%20for%20%26quot%3Btrusted%26quot%3B%20apps%20could%20be%20a%20viable%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20DPI%20could%20take%20the%20form%20of%20a%20whitelist%20of%20approved%20app%20stores%2C%20allowing%20users%20to%20download%20and%20install%20apps%20from%20these%20vetted%20sources%20without%20encountering%20the%20daunting%20warnings%20and%20roadblocks%20typically%20associated%20with%20%26quot%3Buntrusted%26quot%3B%20sources.%20This%20approach%20would%20not%20only%20provide%20greater%20choice%20to%20consumers%20but%20also%20encourage%20app%20stores%20to%20adhere%20to%20transparent%20and%20fair%20policies%20in%20order%20to%20gain%20the%20coveted%20%26quot%3Btrusted%26quot%3B%20status.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20this%20DPI%20is%20simple%20to%20build.%20We%20could%20get%20the%20tech%20running%20in%20less%20than%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Idea%20Not%20Without%20Challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20even%20this%20solution%20is%20not%20without%20its%20policy%20challenges.%20Thorny%20governance%20issues%20surrounding%20the%20maintenance%20of%20such%20a%20whitelist%20and%20ensuring%20the%20integrity%20of%20approved%20app%20stores%20would%20need%20to%20be%20addressed.%20Nonetheless%2C%20these%20might%20be%20surmountable.%20We%20can%20have%20simple%20reporting%20requirements%20and%20adjudication%20via%20Online%20Dispute%20Resolution%20to%20surface%20and%20resolve%20disputes%20between%20app%20builders%20and%20app%20stores.%20This%20targeted%20intervention%20could%20strike%20a%20delicate%20balance%2C%20respecting%20the%20investments%20and%20innovations%20of%20tech%20giants%20while%20also%20ensuring%20a%20level-playing%20field%20for%20local%20developers%20and%20fostering%20a%20more%20vibrant%20and%20competitive%20app%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20India%20has%20had%20great%20success%20with%20UPI%2C%20and%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI)%20deserves%20to%20take%20a%20bow%2C%20we%20can't%20take%20the%20same%20success%20for%20granted%20for%20each%20DPI%20we%20attempt.%20One%20key%20feature%20that%20I%20would%20attribute%20UPI's%20success%20to%20was%20the%20simplicity%20of%20its%20architecture%2C%20the%20elegance%20of%20the%20solution%20being%20the%20lightness%20of%20its%20protocol.%20If%20we%20really%20want%20a%20competitive%20app%20store%20ecosystem%2C%20we%20must%20recognise%20what%20functions%20must%20remain%20with%20the%20private%20market%2C%20and%20what%20functions%20are%20suited%20to%20the%20layer%20of%20Infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20through%20such%20a%20balanced%20and%20forward-looking%20approach%20can%20India%20truly%20unlock%20the%20full%20potential%20of%20its%20burgeoning%20app%20ecosystem%20and%20cement%20its%20position%20as%20a%20leading%20force%20in%20the%20digital%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Tanuj%20Bhojwani%20is%20currently%20the%20head%20of%20People%2Bai%2C%20a%20not-for-profit%20working%20on%20AI%20for%20good.%20Since%202016%2C%20he%20has%20been%20working%20on%20various%20technical%2C%20legal%20and%20policy%20aspects%20of%20Digital%20Public%20Infrastructure%20with%20Nandan%20Nilekani%2C%20with%20whom%20he%20has%20also%20co-authored%20a%20book%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Art%20of%20Bitfulness%E2%80%9D.%20He%20is%20currently%20on%20the%20Board%20of%20the%20Digital%20Public%20Goods%20Alliance)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709732040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fpoj0cg2s_google_625x300_09_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%2