%20can%20be%20done%20without%20registering%20on%20the%20NaMo%20app.%20Such%20directives%20from%20DU%20should%20be%20avoided%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.narendramodi.in%2Fen%2Fmobile%2Fprivacy-policy%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCollaboration%252C%2520community%252Dbuilding%2520and%2520connecting%2C%2526%2520grass%252Droot%2520workers%2520themselves.%5C%22%3Eprivacy%20policy%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20the%20NaMo%20app%20community%20states%20the%20following%3A%20%E2%80%9CCollaboration%2C%20community-building%20and%20connecting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20are%20the%20main%20pillars%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20App%20i.e.%20NaMo%20App.%20(%E2%80%98App%E2%80%99).%20The%20NaMo%20App%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98one%20of%20its%20kind%E2%80%99%20app%20which%20is%20powered%20by%20supporters%20%26amp%3B%20fans%20of%20PM%20Modi%2C%20volunteers%20%26amp%3B%20grass-root%20workers%20themselves.%20You%20are%20joining%20millions%20of%20users%20of%20this%20community%20who%20aspire%20for%20a%20New%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20states%20that%20the%20app%20allows%20users%20to%20%E2%80%9Cinteract%20directly%20with%20PM%20Modi%2C%20contribute%20to%20nation%20building%20through%20various%20ways%20and%20connect%20with%20different%20communities%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98Exam%20Warriors%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20NaMo%20App%20keeps%20you%20updated%20about%20the%20initiatives%20and%20achievements%20of%20the%20government%20led%20by%20PM%20Modi.%20You%20can%20also%20connect%20with%20fellow%20volunteers%20and%20organise%20various%20events%20and%20initiatives.%20You%20can%20take%20part%20in%20different%20surveys%20and%20various%20movements%20like%20%E2%80%98Fit%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Sankalp%20Se%20Siddhi%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20Am%20New%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Swachh%20Bharat%E2%80%99%20etc.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20provide%20%E2%80%9Ca%20tailor-made%20and%20personalised%20experience%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20information%20shared%20on%20the%20app%20%E2%80%9Cmaybe%20processed%20and%20analysed%20by%20third%20party%20services%20who%20are%20engaged%20by%20us%20with%20due%20confidentiality%20obligations%20and%20solely%20for%20the%20specific%20purpose%20of%20such%20services%E2%80%9D%2C%20says%20the%20privacy%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20help%20the%20app%20give%20you%20the%20best%20possible%20experience%20by%20showing%20content%20in%20your%20language%20and%20according%20to%20your%20interests.%20For%20example%2C%20based%20on%20the%20location%20data%20collected%2C%20you%20may%20get%20a%20push%20notification%20when%20PM%20Modi%20is%20in%20your%20state%20or%20%5Bwhen%5D%20there%20is%20an%20important%20initiative%20or%20event%20happening%20in%20your%20state.%20Similarly%2C%20based%20on%20your%20previous%20interactions%20within%20the%20app%2C%20you%20may%20receive%20push%20notifications%20based%20on%20your%20interests%20in%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccovert%20election%20campaign%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nandita%20Narain%2C%20former%20president%20of%20DUTA%20and%20FEDCUTA%2C%20and%20president%20of%20the%20Democratic%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Front%2C%20and%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Joint%20Forum%20for%20Movement%20on%20Education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20covert%20election%20campaign%20and%20mandatory%20participation%20makes%20it%20coercive.%20All%20our%20(Delhi%20University)%20official%20spaces%20are%20being%20used%20for%20such%20activities%20and%20such%20use%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20general%20elections%20is%20highly%20inappropriate%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%20last%20year%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20while%20addressing%20the%20Delhi%20University%20during%20its%20centenary%20celebrations%2C%20had%20said%20that%20the%20institution%20should%20make%20India%20%E2%80%9CViksit%20Bharat%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20goal%20of%20Delhi%20University%20should%20be%20to%20make%20India%20%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat%E2%80%99%20(developed%20India)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Fgoal-of-delhi-university-should-be-to-make-india-viksit-bharat-pm-modi-8694718%2F%5C%22%3Ehad%20said.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20standard%20operating%20procedures%20for%20universities%20on%20Delhi%20University%E2%80%99s%20Viksit%20Bharat%202047%20page%20say%20that%E2%80%9D%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat%402047%20is%20the%20vision%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20make%20India%20a%20developed%20nation%20by%202047%2C%20the%20100th%20year%20of%20its%20independence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20urges%20the%20participation%20of%20the%20youth%2C%20and%20also%20says%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CDepartment%20of%20Higher%20Education%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20will%20lead%20the%20communication%20and%20outreach%20in%20this%20regard.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709731858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F27162303%2Fnamo-app-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdus-kalindi-college-asks-students-to-register-on-namo-app-for-event-with-smriti-irani-as-chief-guest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20poster%20by%20Kalindi%20College%20says%20that%20registration%20on%20the%20app%20is%20mandatory%20and%20only%20those%20students%20who%20have%20registered%20on%20the%20app%20will%20get%20%E2%80%9Cmerchandise%2C%20refreshments%2C%20and%20certificates.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdus-kalindi-college-asks-students-to-register-on-namo-app-for-event-with-smriti-irani-as-chief-guest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIndian%20Astronauts%20In%20India-Made%20Rocket...%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Space%20Official%20On%20Gaganyaan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Gaganyaan%20manned%20human%20space%20flight%20mission%20will%20launch%20%26quot%3BIndian%20astronauts%20into%20space%20from%20Indian%20soil%20on%20an%20India-made%20rocket%26quot%3B%2C%20Dr%20Unnikrishnan%20Nair%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20elite%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Center%20in%20Kerala's%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20told%20NDTV%20in%20a%20special%20interview%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpected%20to%20cost%20Rs%209%2C000%20crore%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fgaganyaan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGaganyaan%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20mission%26quot%3B%20that%20will%20send%20four%20specially%20chosen%20and%20trained%20male%20test%20pilots%20from%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20into%20space%2C%20Dr%20Nair%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20flight%20only%20one%2C%20or%20two%2C%20astronauts%20could%20fly%2C%20and%20a%20final%20decision%20on%20this%20has%20yet%20to%20be%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpected%20to%20cost%20Rs%209%2C000%20crore%2C%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20mission%26quot%3B%20that%20will%20send%20four%20specially%20chosen%20and%20trained%20male%20test%20pilots%20from%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20into%20space%2C%20Dr%20Nair%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20tour%20of%20the%20country's%20main%20rocket%20lab%2C%20an%20ultra-secure%20facility%2C%20NDTV%20was%20given%20glimpses%20of%20the%20crew%20module%20-%20in%20which%20one%20or%20two%20of%20the%20four%20pilot-astronauts%20will%20travel%2C%20the%20service%20module%20-%20which%20will%20be%20attached%20to%20the%20former%2C%20and%20the%20space%20suits%20the%C2%A0pilot-astronauts%20will%20wear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crew%20module%20simulator%20-%20in%20which%20astronaut-designates%20are%20currently%20being%20trained%20-%20and%20can%20accommodate%20two%20astronauts%20was%20also%20shown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crew%20module%2C%20Dr%20Nair%20said%2C%20is%20a%20little%20over%2010%20feet%20in%20diameter%20and%20is%20configured%20for%20three%20people%2C%20but%20this%20can%20be%20adjusted%20depending%20on%20mission%20requirements.%20The%20space%20suits%20were%20purchased%20from%20the%20Russians%20as%20part%20of%20a%20deal%20to%20buy%20the%20seats%2C%20which%20follow%20the%20'cradle'%20philosophy%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20test%20pilots%20themselves%2C%20Dr%20Nair%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20know...%20since%20they%20are%20from%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%2C%20they%20are%20close%20to%20astronauts%20in%20terms%20of%20key%20attributes%2C%20like%20quick%20response%20time%2C%20and%20have%20responded%20well%20to%20tests%20like%20centrifuge%2C%20which%20subjects%20them%20to%20higher%20acceleration%20forces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20trained%20at%20are%20now%20an%20astronaut%20training%20centre%20for%2013%20months%20for%20training%20on%20survivability%20in%20different%20conditions%2C%20and%20then%20will%20be%20were%20subjected%20to%20parabolic%20flight%20tests.%20Then%20they%20went%20will%20go%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20where%20a%20the%20Human%20Space%20Flight%20Centre%20is%20set%20up%20and%20will%20get%20more%20training%2C%20including%20physical%20training.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20pilot-astronauts%20-%20dubbed%20'India's%20Fantastic%204'%20-%20were%20revealed%20to%20the%20country%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20last%20week%3B%20they%20are%20Group%20Captains%20Prasanth%20Balakrishnan%20Nair%2C%20Ajit%20Krishnan%2C%20and%20Angad%20Pratap%2C%20and%20Wing%20Commander%20Shubhanshu%20Shukla.%20All%20are%20highly%20experienced%20test%20pilots%2C%20and%20will%20be%20over%2040%20years%20of%20age%20when%20the%20first%20flight%20lifts%20off%20on%20the%20Launch%20Vehicle%20Mark-3.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaganyaan-mission-astronauts-meet-the-4-astronauts-of-indias-crewed-space-mission-gaganyaan-5135754%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia's%20Fantastic%204%3A%20Meet%20Gaganyaan%20Astronauts%20Named%20By%20PM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20training%20will%20also%20include%20academic%20courses%20and%20detailed%20instruction%20on%20Gaganyaan%20flight%20systems%2C%20as%20well%20as%20yoga%2C%20sources%20at%20ISRO%2C%20India's%20space%20agency%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgravity-flying-practice-yoga-rigorous-training-for-4-gaganyaan-astronauts-5143796%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGravity%2C%20Flying%20Practice%2C%20Yoga%3A%20Training%20For%20Gaganyaan%20Astronauts%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20all%20four%20also%20received%20training%20at%20Russia's%20Gagarin%20Cosmonaut%20Training%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Nair%20also%20explained%20why%20no%20women%20will%20be%20part%20of%20this%20historic%20space%20flight%20-%20because%20pilot-astronauts%20are%20drawn%20from%20the%20ranks%20of%20Air%20Force%20test%20pilots.%20At%20this%20time%2C%20India%20has%20no%20women%20in%20that%20role%20as%20test%20pilots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Explains%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaganyaan-isro-explained-why-no-woman-among-4-pilots-chosen-for-gaganyaan-mission-5136599%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhy%20No%20Woman%20Among%204%20Pilots%20Chosen%20For%20Gaganyaan%20Mission%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20HSFC%20(Human%20Space%20Flight%20Centre)%20Director%2C%20we%20put%20this%20idea%20to%20the%20Air%20Force.%20But%20unfortunately%2C%20there%20were%20then%20no%20women%20test%20pilots%20then.%20Now%2C%20I%20understand%20there%20are...%20and%20I%20hope%20they%20will%20soon%20join%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Meanwhile%20Nair%20says%20women%20can%20get%20an%20opportunity%20to%20be%20an%20astronaut%20as%20mission%20specialists%20who%20could%20be%20flown%20after%20the%20technology%20demonstrator%20flights%20are%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20NDTV%20also%20met%20Vyommitra%20-%20the%20robotic%20(female)%20humanoid%20that%20will%20fly%20into%20space%20for%20a%20test%20flight%20ahead%20of%20the%20mission.%20The%20new%20avatar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fvyommitra%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVyommitra%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20made%20of%20metal%20and%20far%20less%20fragile%20looking%20than%20what%20was%20shown%20earlier%20wearing%20Indian%20clothes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20of%20Vyommitra%20-%20whose%20name%20comes%20from%20Sanskrit%20words%20meaning%20'space'%20('%3Cem%3Evyom%3C%2Fem%3E')%20and%20'friend'%20('%3Cem%3Emitra%3C%2Fem%3E')%20-%20may%20be%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%20this%20year.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-robot-astronaut-vyommitra-to-simulate-human-functions-in-space-4993295%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERobot%20Astronaut%20Vyommitra%20To%20Simulate%20Human%20Functions%20In%20Space%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20work%20is%20on%20at%20full%20pace%20for%20the%20Gaganyaan%20mission%2C%20which%20will%20cost%20about%20Rs%209%2C000%20crore%2C%20with%20the%20four%20test%20pilots%20undergoing%20special%20training%20and%20the%20launch%20vehicle%20now%20human%20rated%2C%20which%20means%20its%20ability%20to%20safely%20carry%20and%20return%20its%20human%20occupants%20has%20been%20evaluated%20and%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20manned%20flight%2C%20though%2C%20there%20must%20be%20at%20least%20two%20successful%20unmanned%20flights%2C%20the%20first%20of%20which%2C%20if%20all%20goes%20well%2C%20will%20take%20place%20by%20the%20middle%20of%2C%20or%20end%20of%2C%20this%20year%2C%20NDTV%20was%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%2020%20different%20big%20tests%20need%20to%20be%20completed%20successfully%20and%20back-to-back%20before%20an%20Indian%20astronaut%20can%20be%20launched%20into%20space%20from%20Sriharikota%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20ISRO%20is%20un-willing%20to%20give%20an%20exact%20time%20frame%20for%20the%20crewed%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20though%2C%20may%20not%20happen%20before%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20India%20succeeds%2C%20it%20will%20only%20be%20the%20fourth%20country%20after%20Russia%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20China%20to%20have%20independent%20capability%20to%20launch%20humans%20into%20space%2C%20and%20scientists%20at%20ISRO%20are%20working%20hard%20to%20make%20this%20national%20mission%20a%20success%20in%20this%20year%20of%20Gaganyaan%20readiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709731620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fh3m427j8_pallava-bagla-isro-gaganyaan-exclusive_625x300_06_March_24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaganyaan-news-isro-vikram-sarabhai-space-centre-indian-astronauts-in-india-made-rocket-top-space-official-on-gaganyaan-5187714%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Gaganyaan%20manned%20space%20flight%20mission%20will%20launch%20%26quot%3BIndian%20astronauts%20into%20space%20from%20Indian%20soil%20on%20an%20India-made%20rocket%26quot%3B%2C%20Dr%20Unnikrishnan%20Nair%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20elite%20Vikram%20Sarabhai%20Space%20Center%20in%20Kerala%2C%20told%20NDTV%20in%20a%20special%20interview.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaganyaan-news-isro-vikram-sarabhai-space-centre-indian-astronauts-in-india-made-rocket-top-space-official-on-gaganyaan-5187714%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaganyaan-news-isro-vikram-sarabhai-space-centre-indian-astronauts-in-india-made-rocket-top-space-official-on-gaganyaan-5187714%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaganyaan-news-isro-vikram-sarabhai-space-centre-indian-astronauts-in-india-made-rocket-top-space-official-on-gaganyaan-5187714%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan's%20Ex-PM%20Zulfikar%20Ali%20Bhutto%2C%20Hanged%20in%201979%2C%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Get%20a%20Fair%20Trial%2C%20Rules%20SC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F29103805%2FSupreme_Court_of_Pakistan2.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20on%20Wednesday%20(March%206)%20that%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Zulfikar%20Ali%20Bhutto%2C%20who%20was%20hanged%20in%201979%20after%20being%20convicted%20of%20murder%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20a%20fair%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20find%20that%20the%20fair%20trial%20and%20due%20process%20requirements%20were%20met%2C%E2%80%9D%20Reuters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fpakistans-bhutto-hanged-44-years-ago-didnt-get-fair-trial-rules-top-court-2024-03-06%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20Chief%20Justice%20Qazi%20Faez%20Isa%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nine-member%20bench%20led%20by%20Isa%20consisted%20of%20Justice%20Sardar%20Tariq%20Masood%2C%20Justice%20Syed%20Mansoor%20Ali%20Shah%2C%20Justice%20Yahya%20Afridi%2C%20Justice%20Amin-ud-Din%20Khan%2C%20Justice%20Jamal%20Khan%20Mandokhel%2C%20Justice%20Muhammad%20Ali%20Mazhar%2C%20Justice%20Syed%20Hasan%20Azhar%20Rizvi%20and%20Justice%20Musarrat%20Hilali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proceedings%20were%20broadcast%20live%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.supremecourt.gov.pk%2Fcourt-proceedings%2F%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxVHE-F62J3M%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20announcing%20the%20unanimous%20opinion%2C%20%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1819573%2Fsc-says-conditions-of-fair-trial-due-process-not-met-in-zulfikar-bhuttos-trial%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20Chief%20Justice%20Isa%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20proceedings%20of%20the%20trial%20by%20the%20Lahore%20High%20Court%20and%20of%20the%20appeal%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20Pakistan%20do%20not%20meet%20the%20requirements%20of%20the%20fundamental%20right%20to%20a%20fair%20trial%20and%20due%20process%20enshrined%20in%20Articles%204%20and%209%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20and%20later%20guaranteed%20as%20a%20separate%20and%20fundamental%20right%20under%20Article%2010A%20of%20the%20Constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20newspaper%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20acknowledged%20that%20there%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Csome%20cases%20in%20our%20judicial%20history%20that%20created%20a%20public%20perception%20that%20either%20fear%20or%20favour%20deterred%20the%20performance%20of%20a%20duty%20to%20administer%20justice%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20therefore%20be%20willing%20to%20confront%20our%20past%20missteps%20and%20fallibilities%20with%20humility%2C%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20self-accountability%2C%20and%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20our%20commitment%20to%20ensure%20that%20justice%20must%20be%20served%20with%20unwavering%20integrity%20and%20fidelity%20to%20the%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Isa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20cannot%20correct%20ourselves%20and%20progress%20in%20the%20right%20direction%20until%20we%20acknowledge%20our%20past%20mistakes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20the%20awarding%20and%20maintaining%20of%20the%20death%20sentence%20was%20%E2%80%9Cjustified%20or%20could%20amount%20to%20deliberate%20murder%E2%80%9D%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20Isa%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20court%20cannot%20reappraise%20the%20evidence%20and%20undo%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20case.%20However%2C%20in%20our%20detailed%20reasons%2C%20we%20shall%20identify%20the%20major%20constitutional%20and%20legal%20lapses%20that%20had%20occurred%20with%20regard%20to%20fair%20trial%20and%20due%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20will%20issue%20a%20detailed%20order%20later%2C%20per%20news%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhutto%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20(PPP)%20now%20run%20by%20his%20grandson%20and%20former%20foreign%20minister%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari%2C%20was%20hanged%20in%201979%20after%20a%20trial%20under%20the%20military%20regime%20of%20late%20General%20Zia-ul-Haq.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20hailed%20the%20ruling.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20positive%20development%20that%20a%20wrong%20done%20by%20a%20court%20has%20been%20corrected%20by%20a%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20from%20his%20office%2C%20reported%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20pursuit%20of%20justice%20was%20a%20labour%20of%20love%20by%20President%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%20in%20the%20name%20of%20his%20wife%20Shaheed%20Mohtarma%20Benazir%20Bhutto.%20Our%20family%20waited%203%20generations%20to%20hear%20these%20words.%20Jiya%20Bhutto!%20Long%20live%20Bhutto!%E2%80%9D%20Bhutto%20Zardari%20said%20later%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMore%20than%2044%20years%20after%20judicial%20murder%20and%20more%20than%2012%20years%20after%20presidential%20reference%20was%20filed%3B%20today%20a%20unanimous%20decision%20announce%20by%20CJP%20Isa.%20Shaheed%20Zulfikar%20Ali%20Bhutto%20did%20not%20get%20a%20fair%20trial.%20The%20pursuit%20of%20justice%20was%20a%20labour%20of%20love%20by%20President%20Asif%20Ali%20Zardari%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FrTNgLWeood%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FrTNgLWeood%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20BilawalBhuttoZardari%20(%40BBhuttoZardari)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBBhuttoZardari%2Fstatus%2F1765281795417706802%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%206%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20hoped%20that%2C%2044%20years%20later%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20opinion%20would%20allow%20Pakistan%20to%20progress%2C%20and%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Csystem%E2%80%9D%20would%20finally%20be%20put%20on%20the%20right%20path%2C%20reported%20%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20stain%20of%20this%20decision%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Pakistan%20to%20have%20faith%20in%20the%20court%2C%20and%20get%20justice%20from%20this%20court%2C%20especially%20if%20someone%20like%20the%20prime%20minister%20did%20not%20get%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709731184000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F29103805%2FSupreme_Court_of_Pakistan2.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistans-ex-pm-zulfikar-ali-bhutto-hanged-in-1979-didnt-get-a-fair-trial-rules-sc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'We%20didn't%20find%20that%20the%20fair%20trial%20and%20due%20process%20requirements%20were%20met%2C'%20said%20Chief%20Justice%20Qazi%20Faez%20Isa.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistans-ex-pm-zulfikar-ali-bhutto-hanged-in-1979-didnt-get-a-fair-trial-rules-sc%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pilot%20Injured%20After%20Trainer%20Aircraft%20Crashes%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Guna%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20pilot%20has%20been%20injured%20after%20a%20trainer%20aircraft%20crashed%20in