2Fen%2Flive-news%2F20240305-gaza-s-starving-children-need-a-flood-of-aid-un%5C%22%3Eat%20least%2010%20children%20had%20died%20due%20to%20starvation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20Ahmed%20Dahir%2C%20who%20headed%20the%20mission.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20health%20ministry%20later%20updated%20the%20number%20of%20child%20deaths%20at%20the%20hospital%20to%2015%2C%20with%20an%20additional%20six%20acutely%20malnourished%20infants%20in%20critical%20condition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELaerke%20pleaded%20for%20immediate%20action%2C%20urging%20the%20international%20community%20to%20%E2%80%9Cflood%20Gaza%20with%20aid%E2%80%9D%20to%20alleviate%20the%20growing%20humanitarian%20crisis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20the%20latest%20escalation%20in%20Gaza%2C%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F03%2F1147227%5C%22%3E500%20trucks%20a%20day%20entered%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20daily%20tally%20in%20recent%20months%20and%20days%20has%20barely%20risen%20above%20133%2C%20Laerke%20explained.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20UN%20assessment%20in%20January%20revealed%20alarming%20levels%20of%20malnutrition%20among%20children%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMalnutrition%20%E2%80%93%20which%20leads%20to%20irreparable%20wasting%20in%20young%20children%20%E2%80%93%20was%20never%20the%20deadly%20threat%20in%20Gaza%20that%20it%20is%20now%2C%20as%20the%20enclave%20was%20largely%20self-sufficient%20in%20fish%20and%20other%20food%20production%2C%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20Dr.%20Rik%20Peeperkorn%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20the%20recent%20months%E2%80%99%20hostilities%2C%20wasting%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20was%20rare%20with%20just%200.8%25%20of%20children%20under%20five%20years%20of%20age%20acutely%20malnourished%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20(current)%20rate%20of%2015.6%25%20of%20wasting%20among%20children%20under%20two%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20suggests%20a%20serious%20and%20rapid%20decline.%20Such%20a%20decline%20in%20a%20population%E2%80%99s%20nutritional%20status%20in%20three%20months%20is%20unprecedented%20globally%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F03%2F1147227%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20WHO%20official%20noted%20with%20concern%20that%2090%25%20of%20children%20under%20two%20years%20old%20and%2095%25%20of%20pregnant%20and%20breastfeeding%20women%20%E2%80%9Cface%20severe%20food%20poverty%20%E2%80%93%20meaning%20they%20have%20consumed%20two%20or%20less%20food%20groups%20in%20the%20previous%20day%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20food%20they%20do%20have%20access%20to%20is%20of%20the%20lowest%20nutritional%20value%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709730048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20163806%2Fimage1170x530croppe.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fflood-gaza-with-aid-un-calls-on-international-community-as-children-die-from-starvation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Last%20weekend%2C%20the%20WHO%20revealed%20distressing%20scenes%20of%20starving%20children%20after%20gaining%20access%20to%20two%20northern%20hospitals%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20October.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fflood-gaza-with-aid-un-calls-on-international-community-as-children-die-from-starvation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Calls%20Women%20Of%20Sandeshkhali%20%26quot%3BMaa%20Durga%26quot%3B%2C%20Meets%20Them%2C%20Assures%20Justice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20met%20a%20group%20of%20women%20from%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20where%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20against%20TMC%20leaders%20have%20been%20levelled%2C%20and%20assured%20them%20of%20justice%20and%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20sidelines%20of%20a%20public%20meeting%20at%20Barasat%20in%20Bengal's%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%20where%20Sandeshkhali%20is%20located%2C%20PM%20Modi%20met%20five%20women%20who%20charged%20suspended%20TMC%20leader%20Shajahan%20Sheikh%20and%20his%20followers%20with%20sexually%20harassing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20the%20women%20who%20have%20been%20protesting%20against%20the%20alleged%20atrocities%20as%20'Maa%20Durga'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rally%2C%20organised%20by%20the%20BJP's%20Mahila%20Morcha%2C%20was%20themed%20Nari%20Shakti%20Vandan%20(celebrating%20women's%20empowerment).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScores%20of%20women%20who%20were%20headed%20to%20the%20rally%20venue%20from%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20however%2C%20failed%20to%20meet%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20on%20account%20of%20their%20vehicles%20being%20stopped%20by%20the%20police%20at%20multiple%20locations%20en%20route%2C%20resulting%20in%20delay%20in%20arrival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20women%2C%20along%20with%20their%20accompanying%20BJP%20workers%2C%20were%20seen%20staging%20protests%20against%20the%20state%20administration%20at%20their%20stoppage%20points%20as%20well%20as%20at%20the%20meeting%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20public%20meeting%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20met%20a%20few%20women%20from%20Sandeshkhali.%20The%20women%20spoke%20about%20the%20atrocities%20that%20were%20perpetrated%20on%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20state%20general%20secretary%20Agnimitra%20Paul%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20over%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20called%20us%20Maa%20Durga%20and%20showered%20his%20respect%20for%20us%20when%20we%20went%20into%20his%20backstage%20enclosure%20to%20touch%20his%20feet%20and%20narrate%20our%20plight%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20victims%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20representing%20the%20womenfolk%20of%20Sandeshkhali%20who%20were%20allegedly%20tormented%20and%20abused%20by%20Trinamool%20leader%20Shajahan%20Sheikh%20and%20his%20cohorts%20later%20said%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20assured%20them%20of%20all%20safety%20and%20security%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20sources%20said%20the%20women%20turned%20emotional%20while%20narrating%20their%20ordeal%20to%20the%20PM%20who%20heard%20them%20patiently%20%26quot%3Blike%20a%20father%20figure%26quot%3B.%20He%20understood%20their%20pain%2C%20party%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20asked%20our%20names%20and%20the%20names%20of%20the%20villages%20where%20we%20live.%20We%20revealed%20to%20him%20the%20names%20of%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20the%20crimes%20and%20told%20him%20about%20the%20insecurity%20we%20continue%20to%20live%20in.%20He%20told%20us%20not%20to%20worry%20and%20expressed%20his%20respect%20for%20the%20fight%20we%20have%20put%20up%20against%20those%20criminals%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20female%20Sandeshkhali%20resident%20stated%20after%20meeting%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20requested%20him%20to%20ensure%20that%20we%20get%20justice%20since%20we%20no%20longer%20have%20faith%20in%20the%20state%20administration.%20The%20PM%2C%20despite%20his%20busy%20schedule%2C%20gave%20us%20a%20patient%20hearing.%20We%20are%20hopeful%20about%20getting%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20women%20protestor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20several%20buses%20in%20which%20women%20from%20Sandeshkhali%20were%20travelling%20to%20the%20PM's%20rally%20were%20stopped%20at%20multiple%20places%20by%20the%20police%20citing%20%26quot%3Bsecurity%20protocol%26quot%3B%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20BJP%20had%20made%20arrangements%20for%20the%20buses%20to%20transport%20the%20women%2C%20who%20were%20allegedly%20tortured%20by%20suspended%20TMC%20leader%20Shajahan%20Sheikh%20and%20his%20aides%2C%20from%20Sandeshkhali%20to%20the%20rally%20venue%2C%20around%2080%20km%20away%2C%20and%20meet%20the%20PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20buses%20were%20first%20stopped%20at%20the%20Biswa%20Bangla%20Gate%20in%20New%20Town%2C%20and%20then%20again%20at%20Airport%20Gate%201%20on%20the%20way%20to%20Barasat%2C%20citing%20security%20protocol%2C%20while%20other%20vehicles%20were%20allowed.%20The%20police%20are%20trying%20to%20stop%20us%20from%20reaching%20the%20PM's%20rally%20on%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BJP%20leader%20who%20was%20on%20one%20of%20the%20buses%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20traffic%20movement%20on%20the%20stretch%20had%20to%20be%20restricted%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bsecurity%20protocol%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20PM%20was%20to%20travel%20by%20that%20road%20after%20exiting%20from%20the%20NSC%20Bose%20International%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20traffic%20movement%20on%20the%20entire%20stretch%20was%20restricted%20due%20to%20security%20reasons.%20The%20buses%20reached%20the%20area%20when%20the%20PM's%20convoy%20was%20about%20to%20arrive%2C%20and%20hence%20the%20movement%20was%20regulated%20for%20security%20reasons%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20once%20the%20convoy%20passed%2C%20the%20buses%20were%20allowed%20to%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%2C%20however%2C%20were%20not%20convinced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20police%20deliberately%20stopped%20our%20buses%20at%20three%20points.%20They%20could%20identify%20us%20from%20the%20banners%20we%20had%20hung%20on%20the%20buses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20left%20our%20homes%20at%207%20am%2C%20and%20still%20failed%20to%20reach%20the%20rally%20venue%20on%20time%20to%20meet%20the%20PM%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20disgruntled%20Sandeshkhali%20woman%20told%20PTI%2C%20claiming%20that%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20reach%20the%20rally%20venue%20in%20a%20convoy%20of%20about%2020%20buses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20left%20Barasat%20at%20around%201%3A30%20pm.%20Assuming%20the%20team%20reached%20the%20fag%20end%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20simple%20math%20reveals%20that%20the%20contingent%20took%20more%20than%20six%20hours%20to%20reach%20the%20venue%20when%2C%20under%20normal%20circumstances%2C%20it%20shouldn't%20have%20taken%20them%20more%20than%20three%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20riverine%20island%20of%20Sandeshkhali%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%20has%20been%20on%20the%20boil%20over%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20atrocities%20on%20women%20and%20land%20grabbing%20by%20suspended%20TMC%20leader%20Shajahan%20Sheikh%20and%20his%20associates.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709729580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F0gm4o9s4_narendra-modi-bengal-rally-ani_625x300_06_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-calls-women-of-sandeshkhali-maa-durga-meets-them-assures-justice-5187669%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20met%20a%20group%20of%20women%20from%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20where%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20against%20TMC%20leaders%20have%20been%20levelled%2C%20and%20assured%20them%20of%20justice%20and%20security.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-calls-women-of-sandeshkhali-maa-durga-meets-them-assures-justice-5187669%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-calls-women-of-sandeshkhali-maa-durga-meets-them-assures-justice-5187669%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-calls-women-of-sandeshkhali-maa-durga-meets-them-assures-justice-5187669%2Famp%2F1%2