0Constitution%20in%20which%20secularism%20finds%20a%20mention.%20Our%20court%20system%20may%20have%20been%20created%20by%20the%20British%20but%20it%20is%20run%20by%20our%20Constitution.%20The%20courts%20are%20given%20by%20the%20Constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderlining%20the%20efforts%20he%20had%20made%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20a%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20Karnataka%20high%20court%2C%20Justice%20Oka%20said%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20I%20tried%20many%20times%20to%20reduce%20such%20religious%20programmes%20but%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20stop%20them%20completely.%20But%20completion%20of%2075%20years%20is%20the%20best%20occasion%20for%20us%20to%20advance%20secularism.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709728210000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06133006%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-06-at-1.29.35-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fstop-pooja-archana-during-court-events-bow-down-to-constitution-instead-sc-judge%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Justice%20Oka%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20new%20practice%20should%20be%20started%20as%20the%20Constitution%20completes%2075%20years%20and%20underlined%20that%20the%20words%20'secular'%20and%20'democratic'%20in%20the%20Preamble%20are%20very%20important%20for%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fstop-pooja-archana-during-court-events-bow-down-to-constitution-instead-sc-judge%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Surat%20Cops%20Question%20SunRisers%20Hyderabad%20Cricketer%20In%20Model%20Suicide%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPolice%20questioned%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20cricketer%20%3Ca%2