%20on%20its%20own%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20party%20knows%20that%20states%20where%20it%20did%20not%20manage%20to%20do%20very%20well%20in%20the%20last%20polls%20will%20hold%20the%20key.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20begun%20translating%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20speeches%20to%20Kannada%2C%20Tamil%2C%20Telugu%2C%20Malayalam%2C%20Bengali%2C%20Odia%2C%20Punjabi%20and%20Marathi%20in%20real%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20the%20fact%20that%20four%20of%20the%20eight%20languages%20are%20southern%20is%20no%20accident.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%20only%2029%20of%20the%20129%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20(130%20including%20Puducherry)%20in%20the%20southern%20states%20and%20most%20of%20these%20had%20come%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20swept%20to%20power%20in%20the%20last%20Assembly%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20had%20been%20used%20during%20the%20Kashi%20Tamil%20Sangamam%20in%20December%20last%20year%20as%20well%2C%20when%20PM%20Modi's%20speech%20had%20been%20translated%20into%20Tamil.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20new%20beginning%20and%2C%20hopefully%2C%20it%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20me%20to%20reach%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20told%20his%20listeners%20at%20the%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20translating%20the%20PM's%20speeches%20will%20make%20a%20difference%2C%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20MP%20K%20Raghu%20Rama%20Krishna%20Raju%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20have%20a%20huge%20impact.%20People%20in%20the%20south%2C%20we%20like%20our%20local%20languages%2C%20and%20if%20it%20appears%20that%20anybody%20is%20interacting%20with%20us%20in%20our%20language%2C%20we%20love%20them.%20A%20towering%20personality%20like%20PM%20Modi%20doing%20so%20will%20win%20over%20the%20hearts%20of%20Telugus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raju's%20remark%20came%20amid%20speculation%20of%20his%20party%20and%20the%20BJP%20forming%20an%20alliance%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumber-Crunching%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20choice%20of%20the%20other%20languages%20is%20also%20strategic.%20Maharashtra%20and%20West%20Bengal%20send%20the%20second-%20and%20third-highest%20number%20of%20MPs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20respectively%2C%20and%20the%20party%20has%20been%20putting%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%20into%20bettering%20its%20numbers%20in%20these%20states.%20In%202019%2C%20it%20had%20won%2023%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20while%20its%20ally%20Shiv%20Sena%20had%20achieved%20victory%20in%2018.%20In%20Bengal%2C%20it%20had%20managed%20to%20win%2018%20of%20the%20state's%2042%20seats%2C%20which%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20big%20victory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Odisha%2C%20the%20party%20had%20won%208%20of%2021%20seats%20and%20it%20had%20bagged%202%20of%20the%2013%20seats%20in%20Punjab.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20translated%20speeches%20will%20be%20available%20on%20certain%20handles%20on%20X%2C%20including%20%40NaMoInBengali%2C%20%40NamoinKannada%2C%20%40NaMoinTamil%2C%20%40NaMoinTelugu%20and%20%40NaMoinMarathi.%20Some%20of%20these%20handles%20also%20have%20the%20PM's%20addresses%20from%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22ta%5C%22%3E%E0%AE%AA%E0%AE%BF%E0%AE%B0%E0%AE%A4%E0%AE%AE%20%E0%AE%AE%E0%AE%A8%E0%AF%8D%E0%AE%A4%E0%AE%BF%E0%AE%B0%E0%AE%BF%20%E0%AE%9A%E0%AF%82%E0%AE%B0%E0%AF%8D%E0%AE%AF%E0%AE%BE%20%E0%AE%95%E0%AE%B0%E0%AF%8D%20%E0%AE%AE%E0%AF%81%E0%AE%83%E0%AE%AA%E0%AF%8D%E0%AE%9F%E0%AF%8D%20%E0%AE%AA%E0%AE%BF%E0%AE%9C%E0%AE%BF%E0%AE%B2%E0%AE%BF%20%E0%AE%AF%E0%AF%8B%E0%AE%9C%E0%AE%A9%E0%AE%BE%20(%E0%AE%AA%E0%AE%BF%E0%AE%B0%E0%AE%A4%E0%AE%AE%E0%AE%B0%E0%AE%BF%E0%AE%A9%E0%AF%8D%20%E0%AE%87%E0%AE%B2%E0%AE%B5%E0%AE%9A%