20the%20ensuing%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%2C%20UOFA%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20launch%20a%20series%20of%20protests%20if%20the%20citizenship%20act%20is%20implemented%20in%20Assam%20including%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98gherao%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20Janata%20Bhawan%20in%20Guwahati%2C%20the%20administrative%20headquarters%20of%20the%20state%2C%20while%20the%20All%20Assam%20Students%20Union%20(AASU)%20declared%20agitations%20if%20the%20Modi%20government%20enacts%20it%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImplementation%20of%20the%20CAA%20in%20Assam%20is%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Assam%20Accord%20of%201985%20as%20per%20which%20anyone%2C%20Hindu%20or%20Muslim%2C%20who%20had%20entered%20the%20state%20from%20Bangladesh%20after%20March%201971%20would%20be%20deemed%20a%20non-citizen.%20The%20Accord%20was%20signed%20with%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20government%20after%20six%20years%20of%20anti-foreigner%20agitation%20in%20the%20state%20which%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%20860%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUOFA%E2%80%99s%20letter%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20signed%20by%20state%20Congress%20leader%20Bhupen%20Borah%20who%20is%20also%20the%20president%20of%20the%2016-party%20forum%20%E2%80%93%20was%20shared%20with%20media%20persons%20in%20Guwahati%20on%20March%204.%20The%20letter%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20strong%20perception%20among%20the%20people%20of%20Assam%20irrespective%20of%20caste%2C%20creed%20and%20political%20affiliation%20that%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%202019%20will%20put%20in%20danger%20the%20culture%2C%20history%2C%20socio-economic%20condition%2C%20social%20fabric%20and%20identity%20of%20Assamese%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frules-under-caa-now-ready-likely-to-be-notified-before-2024-elections-reports%5C%22%3ERules%20Under%20CAA%20Now%20Ready%2C%20Likely%20to%20Be%20Notified%20Before%202024%20Elections%3A%20Reports%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStating%20that%20the%20CAA%20would%20go%20on%20to%20nullify%20the%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%20Assam%20Accord%20of%201985%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20letter%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Accord%20is%20regarded%20as%20the%20lifeline%20of%20the%20Assamese%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeeking%20an%20appointment%20with%20Modi%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20earliest%E2%80%9D%2C%20preferably%20during%20his%20March%208-9%20visit%20to%20the%20state%2C%20UOFA%E2%80%99s%20letter%20warned%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvolatile%20situation%20(is)%20likely%20to%20arise%20in%20Assam%20in%20the%20coming%20days%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2029%2C%20UOFA%20had%20also%20submitted%20a%20letter%20on%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20state%20governor%20marked%20for%20President%20Draupadi%20Murmu.%20The%20letter%2C%20in%20which%20her%20intervention%20was%20sought%20to%20not%20implement%20CAA%20in%20Assam%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20the%20opposition%20political%20parties%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Assam%20have%20been%20opposing%20very%20clearly%20and%20loudly%20the%20unconstitutional%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%202019%20from%20the%20day%20one%20of%20its%20introduction%20in%20the%20Parliament.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20stated%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20government%20taking%20advantage%20of%20its%20majority%20in%20both%20the%20houses%20of%20Parliament%20passed%20the%20bill%20ignoring%20the%20sentiment%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Assam.%20Now%2C%20the%20honourable%20union%20home%20minister%20very%20recently%20declared%20that%20the%20CAA%20is%20going%20to%20be%20implemented%20in%20Assam%20before%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECalling%20it%20%E2%80%9Cunconstitutional%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%E2%80%9D%2C%20UOFA%20urged%20her%20to%20repeal%20the%20Act.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%2016%20parties%20of%20UOFA%20are%20Congress%2C%20Raijor%20Dal%2C%20Asam%20Jatiya%20Parishad%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20Assam%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20CPI%20(M)%2C%20CPI%2C%20All%20India%20Forward%20Bloc%2C%20CPI%20(M-L)%2C%20NCP%20%E2%80%93%20Sharad%20Pawar%20(Assam)%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(Assam)%2C%20Purbanchalio%20Lok%20Parishad%2C%20Jatiya%20Dal%2C%20APHLC%20(Assam)%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Assam)%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(Assam).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709726407000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20094201%2FUntitled-design-15.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fvolatile-situation-likely-to-arise-if-caa-implemented-16-assam-opposition-parties-to-modi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Public%20resistance%20to%20the%20CAA%20has%20returned%20to%20the%20forefront%20in%20Assam%20after%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20announced%20the%20plan%20to%20notify%20and%20implement%20the%20citizenship%20act%20last%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fvolatile-situation-likely-to-arise-if-caa-implemented-16-assam-opposition-parties-to-modi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ChatGPT-maker%20OpenAI%20hits%20back%20at%20Musk%20criticism%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709726364000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F57DE%2Fproduction%2F_132849422_gettyimages-2044112209.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-68488230%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22OpenAI%20rejects%20claims%20it%20is%20focusing%20too%20much%20on%20profit%2C%20sayi