0the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20today%20set%20a%20new%20deadline%20for%20the%20Bengal%20cops%20to%20hand%20him%20over%20to%20the%20central%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Harish%20Tandon%20and%20Justice%20Hiranmay%20Bhattacharyya%20has%20now%20asked%20Bengal%20police%20to%20hand%20over%20Shahjahan's%20custody%20to%20CBI%20by%204.15%20pm%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20had%20yesterday%20asked%20Bengal%20police%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20expelled%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20to%20the%20CBI%20by%204%2C30%20pm.%20The%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20challenged%20the%20ruling%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20When%20a%20CBI%20team%20reached%20to%20take%20Shahjahan's%20custody%20yesterday%2C%20it%20was%20told%20that%20the%20matter%20is%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20however%2C%20turned%20down%20the%20Bengal%20government's%20request%20for%20an%20urgent%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20said%20that%20the%20high%20court%20order%20is%20against%20the%20concept%20of%20federalism.%20Appearing%20for%20the%20Bengal%20government%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BUrgency%20is%20that%20they%20wanted%20overnight%20compliance%20in%20an%20interim%20order.%26quot%3B%20A%20bench%20led%20by%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20has%20now%20asked%20the%20state%20government%20to%20raise%20the%20matter%20before%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20for%20listing%20of%20the%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20today%20noted%20that%20it%20is%20serious%20about%20the%20implementation%20of%20its%20order.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20not%20ordered%20a%20stay.%20So%20Shahjahan%20must%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20CBI%20by%204.15%20pm%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20also%20issued%20a%20notice%20of%20contempt%20and%20asked%20the%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Department%20of%20Bengal%20police%20to%20file%20an%20affidavit%20within%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20had%20approached%20the%20high%20court%20against%20Bengal%20police%20and%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20not%20heard%20the%20state%20government's%20petition%20yet%20and%20there%20is%20no%20pause%20on%20the%20high%20court's%20ruling%20yesterday.%20The%20ED%20has%20also%20sought%20action%20against%20officers%20of%20Bengal's%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Department%20for%20not%20following%20the%20high%20court's%20orders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Shahjahan%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20political%20storm%20surrounding%20Sandeshkhali%20island%20in%20Bengal's%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district.%20Residents%20of%20the%20island%20have%20accused%20Shahjahan%20and%20his%20aides%20of%20harassment%2C%20land%20grab%20and%20extortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strongman%20first%20made%20headlines%20in%20January%20when%20an%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20team%20came%20under%20a%20mob%20attack%20during%20a%20raid%20on%20his%20properties.%20He%20was%20then%20on%20the%20run%20for%2052%20days%20before%20Bengal%20police%20arrested%20him.%20The%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20been%20accusing%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20of%20shielding%20the%20strongman%20and%20has%20stressed%20that%20only%20a%20probe%20by%20the%20central%20agencies%20would%20ensure%20justice%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Sandeshkhali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20has%20expelled%20Shahjahan%20for%20six%20years.%20Hitting%20back%20at%20the%20BJP%20charge%2C%20it%20has%20questioned%20why%20the%20central%20agencies%20could%20not%20arrest%20the%20strongman%20for%20so%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709724840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fa4aeion8_sheikh-shahjahan_625x300_29_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-government-directed-to-hand-over-sheikh-shahjahan-to-cbi-by-4-15-pm-5186826%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20has%20directed%20the%20Bengal%20government%20to%20hand%20over%20Sandeshkhali%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20by%204.15%20pm%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-government-directed-to-hand-over-sheikh-shahjahan-to-cbi-by-4-15-pm-5186826%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-government-directed-to-hand-over-sheikh-shahjahan-to-cbi-by-4-15-pm-5186826%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-government-directed-to-hand-over-sheikh-shahjahan-to-cbi-by-4-15-pm-5186826%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Peter%20Sellers%20Came%20to%20Cambridge%20to%20Address%20the%20India%20Society%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06141034%2F77d4d45b-2941-4222-834c-444ba4229e13.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EMani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%2C%20a%20close%20friend%20through%20school%2C%20college%20and%20university%20(we%20are%20roughly%20the%20same%20age%2C%2083)%20has%20mentioned%20me%20in%20the%20first%20volume%20of%20his%20autobiography%2C%20%3Cem%3EMemoirs%20of%20a%20Maverick%3A%20The%20First%20Fifty%20Years%20(1941%20to%201991)%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20incident%20relates%20to%20the%20late%20actor%2C%20Peter%20Sellers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMani%20and%20I%20were%20then%20undergraduates%20at%20Cambridge%20University.%20He%20was%20studying%20economics%2C%20I%20was%20studying%20history.%20We%20were%20in%20our%20final%20year.%20Mani%20had%20been%20elected%20secretary%20of%20the%20Cambridge%20Union%2C%20the%20prime%20debating%20society%20of%20the%20university%2C%20where%20future%20British%20prime%20ministers%20had%20spoken%20as%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20had%20been%20elected%20president%20of%20the%20Cambridge%20India%20Society%2C%20where%20Indians%20studying%20and%20teaching%20at%20the%20university%20used%20to%20meet.%20My%20job%20was%20also%20to%20invite%20eminent%20speakers%20to%20address%20us%20once%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20challenging%20task%20as%20the%20India%20Society%20had%20been%20in%20the%20red%20for%20many%20years.%20Even%20inviting%20the%20then%20well-known%20editor%20of%20the%20influential%20and%20highly%20respected%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Statesman%20and%20Nation%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Kingsley%20Martin%2C%20could%20not%20attract%20a%20larger%20paying%20audience%20than%20the%20usual%2030%20or%2040.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECamellia%20Panjabi%2C%20another%20contemporary%2C%20who%20was%20then%20the%20secretary-designate%20of%20the%20India%20Society%2C%20and%20went%20on%20to%20join%20the%20Tata%20Administrative%20Service%20(TAS)%20and%20became%20a%20key%20figure%20in%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20Taj%20group%20of%20hotels%2C%20said%20one%20day%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20try%20and%20get%20Peter%20Sellers%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESellers%20was%20then%20one%20of%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20leading%20comedians%2C%20famous%20for%20a%20popular%20radio%20programme%2C%20called%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Goon%20Show%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20had%20starred%20in%20some%20critically%20acclaimed%20British%20films%2C%20including%20the%20classic%20black%20comedy%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Ladykillers%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20which%20Alec%20Guinness%20also%20acted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESellers%2C%20however%2C%20truly%20hit%20big%20time%20internationally%20opposite%20Sophia%20Loren%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Millionairess%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20was%20based%20on%20a%20story%20by%20George%20Bernard%20Shaw%20and%20released%20in%201960.%20He%20played%20the%20role%20of%20an%20Indian%20doctor%2C%20and%20spoke%20in%20what%20was%20considered%20as%20the%20typical%20sing-song%20Indian%20accent.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20many%20of%20my%20English%20university%20friends%20would%20try%20to%20get%20a%20laugh%20by%20conversing%20in%20the%20same%20accent%20when%20talking%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInviting%20Peter%20Sellers%20was%20a%20long%20shot%20but%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20go.%20To%20my%20surprise%2C%20I%20did%20not%20get%20an%20immediate%20%E2%80%9CNo%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20a%20cautious%20response%20from%20his%20secretary.%20So%2C%20I%20pursued%20the%20matter%20and%20then%2C%20to%20my%20huge%20delight%2C%20she%20told%20me%20that%20he%20had%20agreed%20to%20drive%20down%20from%20London%20to%20Cambridge%20to%20address%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fmani-shankar-aiyar-memoirs%5C%22%3EA%20Profile%20in%20Courage%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20hired%20the%20largest%20hall%20available%2C%20the%20Cambridge%20Union%20building%20where%20it%20held%20its%20debates%20and%20which%20could%20hold%20several%20hundred%20people.%20We%20charged%20a%20small%20entrance%20fee%20of%20two%20shillings%2C%20I%20seem%20to%20recall%20(the%20equivalent%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%20Rs%2010)%2C%20but%20so%20big%20was%20the%20rush%20that%20we%20had%20to%20turn%20quite%20a%20few%20students%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20probably%20the%20biggest%20number%20of%20people%20ever%20to%20attend%20an%20India%20Society%20meeting.%20More%20importantly%2C%20it%20got%20the%20society%20out%20of%20the%20red%2C%20even%20leaving%20behind%20a%20healthy%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20over%20one-and-a-half%20hours%2C%20Sellers%20had%20the%20overflowing%20hall%20in%20splits.%20Being%20the%20wonderful%20mimic%20he%20was%2C%20he%20spoke%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20different%20English%20accents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20they%20included%20the%20Indian%20one%2C%20but%20the%20French%20as%20well%2C%20which%20he%20would%20use%20to%20marvellous%20effect%20in%20the%20wildly%20successful%20%3Cem%3EPink%20Panther%3C%2Fem%3E%20series%20of%20films%2C%20where%20he%20played%20the%20bumbling%20French%20detective%2C%20Inspector%20Clouseau.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoincidentally%2C%20when%20Mani%20was%20writing%20his%20memoir%2C%20and%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20could%20remember%20the%20date%20of%20the%20memorable%20Sellers%E2%80%99%20function%2C%20I%20was%20rummaging%20through%20old%20files%20and%20newspaper%20clippings%2C%20trying%20to%20put%20them%20in%20some%20kind%20of%20order.%20And%20there%2C%20I%20found%20my%20university%20diary%20of%201961-62%2C%20and%20a%20yellowed%20clipping%20from%20a%20local%20paper%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ECambridge%20Daily%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20reporting%20the%20event!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20dated%20June%2012%2C%20so%20clearly%20Sellers%20had%20addressed%20the%20India%20Society%20the%20previous%20evening%20on%20June%2012%2C%201962%2C%20almost%2060%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20virtual%20lifetime%2C%20when%20I%20was%2021.%20I%20even%20found%20the%20brief%20hand-written%20speech%20I%20had%20delivered%20to%20introduce%20Sellers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpv-narasimha-rao-mani-shankar-aiyar-book-launch%5C%22%3EP.V.%20Narasimha%20Rao%20Was%20%E2%80%98First%20BJP%20PM%E2%80%99%20of%20India%2C%20Says%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%2C%20Camelia%2C%20Brian%20Pollitt%2C%20a%20close%20friend%20who%20was%20then%20president%20of%20the%20Cambridge%20Union%20(his%20father%2C%20Harry%20Pollitt%2C%20was%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20British%20Communist%20Party)%2C%20Romi%20Khosla%2C%20another%20contemporary%20of%20mine%20at%20Cambridge%20who%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20famous%20architect%2C%20and%20I%20took%20Sellers%20out%20for%20dinner%20to%20a%20small%20Indian%20restaurant%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20brought%20along%20Mario%20Fabrizi%2C%20an%20actor%20friend.%20At%20the%20dinner%20he%20revealed%20that%20the%20director%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Millionairess%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20originally%20wanted%20him%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20an%20Egyptian%20doctor%2C%20but%20he%20persuaded%20the%20director%20to%20change%20it%20to%20an%20Indian%20doctor%20because%2C%20as%20Sellers%20told%20us%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20got%20to%20know%20many%20Indian%20doctors%20and%20liked%20them%20a%20lot.%E2%80%9D%20He%20also%20made%20a%20startling%20confession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDid%20you%20know%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked%20us%20rhetorically%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%20this%20has%20been%20the%20first%20time%20I%20have%20ever%20spoken%20in%20public%3F%20I%20was%20so%20nervous%20at%20the%20prospect%20that%20I%20brought%20Mario%20along%2C%20in%20case%20I%20broke%20down%20and%20could%20not%20continue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20needn%E2%80%99t%20have%20worried.%20He%20had%20held%20all%20of%20us%20completely%20spellbound%20with%20his%20masterly%20mimicry.%20Sadly%2C%20Sellers%20died%20relatively%20young%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2054%2C%20while%20still%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMani%2C%20thank%20you%20for%20the%20memories.%20And%20we%20are%20all%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20next%20volume%20of%20your%20memoirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERahul%20Singh%20served%20as%20an%20assistant%20editor%20at%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3ETimes%20of%20India%20%3Cem%3Eand%20editor%20at%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3EReader%E2%80%99s%20Digest.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709724638000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06141034%2F77d4d45b-2941-4222-834c-444ba4229e13.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fwhen-peter-sellers-came-to-cambridge-to-address-the-india-society%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20author%20recalls%20an%20audacious%20attempt%20by%20him%20to%20invite%20the%20film%20star%20to%20speak%20to%20students.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fwhen-peter-sellers-came-to-cambridge-