%20the%20Maldives%20to%20provide%20free%20military%20assistance%20to%20foster%20%26quot%3Bstronger%26quot%3B%20bilateral%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia-Maldives%20ties%20have%20suffered%20a%20setback%20ever%20since%20Mr%20Muizzu%2C%20who%20is%20blindly%20pro-China%2C%20assumed%20office%20last%20year.%20Hours%20after%20he%20took%20oath%20in%20November%202023%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20steps%20Mr%20Muizzu%20took%2C%20was%20to%20demand%20India%20to%20withdraw%20all%20its%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Muizzu's%20new%20announcement%20comes%20days%20after%20a%20Chinese%20research%20and%20'spy'%20vessel%20spent%20about%20a%20week%20around%20Male%20and%20more%20than%20a%20month%20just%20outside%20Maldives'%20EEZ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20ceremony%20at%20one%20of%20the%20islands%20that%20he%20was%20visiting%20on%20Monday%2C%20Mr%20Muizzu%20said%2C%20the%20Maldives%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20is%20making%20efforts%20to%20obtain%20the%20facilities%20required%20for%20conducting%20the%20hydrographic%20surveys%20by%20the%20country%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20allow%20Maldives%20to%20conduct%20the%20underwater%20surveys%20of%20the%20country%20by%20ourselves.%20We%20will%20then%20acquire%20all%20insights%20of%20our%20underwater%20features%20and%20prepare%20charts%2C%20they%20will%20be%20drawn%20by%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20president%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20Edition.mv%2C%20a%20news%20portal%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaldives'%20former%20administration%2C%20led%20by%20then%20President%20Ibrahim%20Mohamed%20Solih%2C%20had%20signed%20an%20agreement%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20conduct%20hydrographic%20surveys%20of%20Maldives'%20underwater%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20decided%20not%20to%20renew%20the%20agreement%20entered%20into%20with%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20scan%20and%20acquire%20all%20insights%20into%20our%20underwater%20bodies.%20All%20these%20underwater%20details%20are