20to%20make%20them%20whole%2C%20but%20today's%20message%20sends%20a%20message%20loud%20and%20clear%20to%20those%20looking%20to%20introduce%20guns%20on%20our%20streets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20Nasrat%20Ahmad%20Yar%20was%20in%20his%20black%20Toyota%20Highlander%2C%20parked%20a%20block%20south%20of%20Maryland%20Avenue%20NE%20in%20the%20Capitol%20Hill%20neighbourhood.%20He%20had%20just%20completed%20a%20ride%20for%20a%20passenger%20when%20he%20was%20approached%20by%20a%20group%20of%20teenagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teens%20%26quot%3Bmay%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20take%20his%20vehicle%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Parsons%20said%2C%20and%20shot%20him%20in%20that%20interaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20just%20killed%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20person%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%20footage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMateen%20Rahmati%2C%20Ahmad%20Yar's%2033-year-old%20cousin%2C%20said%20that%20police%20notified%20his%20family%20Friday%20of%20an%20arrest%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20relief%20for%20the%20family%20in%20Afghanistan%20and%20his%20kids%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahmati%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20relatives%20had%20been%20consistently%20asking%20when%20there%20would%20be%20an%20arrest.%20%26quot%3BHe%20has%20to%20be%20punished%20for%20what%20he%20did.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709722440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F6835sp0g_us-police-generic_625x300_27_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teen-charged-with-first-degree-murder-of-a-lyft-driver-5187267%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BYou%20just%20killed%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20person%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%20footage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teen-charged-with-first-degree-murder-of-a-lyft-driver-5187267%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%2