2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68488962.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68488962.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20Points%20On%20Smriti%20Irani%2C%20BJP's%20Candidate%20From%20Amethi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20will%20seek%20reelection%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20the%202024%20polls%20from%20the%20high-profile%20Amethi%20seat%2C%20once%20considered%20a%20bastion%20of%20the%20Gandhi-Nehru%20family.%20In%20the%202019%20polls%2C%20Smriti%20Irani%20defeated%20then%20Congress%20President%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20an%20intense%20electoral%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%205%20facts%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20Smriti%20Irani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20Born%20on%20March%2023%2C%201976%2C%20Smriti%20Irani%20started%20her%20career%20as%20a%20model%20and%20was%20one%20of%20the%20finalists%20in%20the%20Miss%20India%20beauty%20pageant%20of%201998.%20She%20got%20her%20breakthrough%20in%20acting%20with%20the%20lead%20role%20of%20Tulsi%20Virani%20in%20Ekta%20Kapoor's%20popular%20daily%20soap%20Kyunki%20Saas%20Bhi%20Kabhi%20Bahu%20Thi.%20She%20was%20also%20seen%20in%20TV%20shows%20like%20Kya%20Hadsaa%20kya%20Haqeeqat%2C%20Ek%20Thi%20Nyaaka%20and%20many%20more%2C%20it%20was%20the%20portrayal%20of%20Tulsi%20Virani%20that%20made%20her%20a%20household%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20Following%20a%20successful%20acting%20career%20in%20television%2C%20Smriti%20Irani%20moved%20to%20active%20politics%20in%202003.%20She%20joined%20the%20BJP%20and%20was%20appointed%20the%20Vice%20President%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20Youth%20Wing%20of%20the%20party%20in%202004.%20She%20contested%20the%202004%20general%20election%20from%20Delhi's%20Chandni%20Chowk%20constituency%20but%20lost%20to%20Congress'%20Kapil%20Sibal.%20She%20was%20named%20the%20National%20President%20of%20the%20BJP%20Mahila%20Morcha%20in%202010.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20she%20was%20elected%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20from%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20In%202014%2C%20Smriti%20Irani%20was%20fielded%20by%20the%20BJP%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Amethi%20Lok%20Sabha%20against%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20had%20won%20the%20seat%20twice.%20Ms%20Irani%20managed%20to%20stir%20up%20a%20contest%20on%20a%20seat%20considered%20a%20bastion%20of%20the%20Gandhi-Nehru%20family%20and%20cut%20down%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20winning%20margin%20to%20just%20over%201%20lakh%20votes.%20Despite%20the%20defeat%2C%20she%20was%20inducted%20into%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20first%20cabinet%20as%20the%20Minister%20of%20Human%20Resource%20Development.%20At%2038%2C%20she%20was%20also%20the%20youngest%20minister%20in%20PM%20Modi's%20first%20cabinet.%20From%202014%20to%202019%2C%20Smriti%20Irani%20held%20the%20portfolios%20of%20HRD%2C%20Textiles%2C%20and%20Information%20%26amp%3B%20Broadcasting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4)%20In%202019%2C%20Irani%20emerged%20as%20a%20giant%20killer%2C%20defeating%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20from%20Amethi.%20Despite%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20alliance%20not%20fielding%20candidates%20in%20support%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Smriti%20Irani%20secured%20a%20victory%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20over%2050%2C000%20votes.%20She%20was%20appointed%20Union%20Minister%20for%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development.%20She%20has%20also%20held%20the%20portfolio%20of%20Minority%20Affairs%20since%20July%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5)%20Smriti%20Irani%20is%20married%20to%20Parsi%20businessman%20Zubin%20Irani.%20The%20couple%20has%20two%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709721840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fappuuqe4_smriti-irani-pti_625x300_06_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-smriti-irani-to-seek-reelection-from-amethi-5-facts-about-the-union-minister-5180576%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20will%20seek%20reelection%20to%20the%