%2C%20Biren%20Singh%20said%20the%20FMR%20has%20not%20been%20scrapped%20yet.%20%E2%80%9CNonetheless%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20been%20suspending%20the%20FMR%20for%20every%20six%20months%20with%20due%20consent%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesangaiexpress.com%2FEncyc%2F2024%2F3%2F6%2FBy-Our-Staff-ReporterIMPHAL-Mar-5-Even-though-the-Ministry-of-Home-Affairs-has-written-to-the-Ministry-of.html%5C%22%3Ehe%20said.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reply%20to%20a%20question%20by%20MLA%20and%20state%20Congress%20chief%20Meghachandra%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20that%20the%20Manipur%20state%20administration%20had%20suspended%20the%20FMR%20with%20Myanmar%20since%202021%20due%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20and%20the%20arrangement%20has%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20latest%20notification%20for%20suspension%20of%20FMR%20was%20issued%20on%20February%2016%20this%20year.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20is%20expected%20to%20issue%20an%20order%20whereby%20FMR%20would%20be%20scrapped%20totally%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chief%20minister%20told%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20referring%20to%20some%20recent%20media%20reports%20about%20the%20arrest%20of%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrants%20from%20Myanmar%E2%80%9D%20in%20Manipur%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20suspension%20of%20the%20FMR%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20that%20citizens%20of%20the%20two%20countries%20%E2%80%9Ccan%20move%20across%20the%20border%20if%20they%20are%20permitted%20by%20authorities%20of%20both%20the%20countries%20even%20though%20FMR%20has%20been%20suspended.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20has%20been%20a%20longstanding%20demand%20from%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Meitei%20community%20to%20fence%20the%20international%20border%20the%20northeastern%20state%20shares%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20citing%20the%20issue%20of%20%E2%80%98illegal%20immigrants%E2%80%99%20entering%20the%20Indian%20state%20through%20it%2C%20their%20last%20ten-month-long%20ethnic%20strife%20with%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Kuki%20community%20has%20also%20seen%20a%20vociferous%20demand%20to%20not%20only%20fence%20the%20border%20but%20also%20scrap%20the%20FMR%20understanding%20too%2C%20as%20per%20which%20people%20residing%20on%20both%20sides%20can%20cross%20the%20international%20border%20up%20to%2016%20kilometres%20without%20passport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20Meitei%20civil%20society%20groups%20have%20been%20alleging%20that%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20immigrants%E2%80%9D%20have%20intruded%20into%20the%20border%20areas%20populated%20by%20the%20Kuki%20community%2C%20who%20share%20kinship%20with%20those%20across%20the%20international%20boundary%2C%20thereby%20posing%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20population%20of%20the%20majority%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20scrap%20India%E2%80%99s%20FMR%20with%20Myanmar%20has%20been%20welcomed%20by%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20population%20of%20Manipur%2C%20it%20has%20been%20vehemently%20opposed%20not%20only%20by%20the%20Kukis%20of%20the%20state%20but%20also%20by%20the%20Mizos%20and%20Nagas%20across%20Manipur%2C%20Mizoram%20and%20Nagaland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20Mizoram%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fguwahati%2Fnagaland-joins-mizoram-in-opposing-suspension-of-fmr%2Farticleshow%2F108153023.cms%5C%22%3ENagaland%3C%2Fa%3E%20assemblies%20have%20passed%20resolutions%20to%20oppose%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%20citing%20kinship%20with%20the%20people%20across%20the%20international%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMizoram%20chief%20minister%20Lalduhoma%20has%20recently%20met%20Shah%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20the%20matter.%20The%20Naga%20Students%E2%80%99%20Federation%20has%20written%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20to%20intervene%20on%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20total%201%2C643-km-long%20India-Myanmar%20bord