y-retailers-report-high-demand-for-prestige-and-premium-segments-124022901044_1.html%5C%22%3Ebeauty%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fconsumer-gap-in-india-mass-market-lags-premium-soars%2Farticleshow%2F107805171.cms%5C%22%3Eare%20seeing%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20enormous%20growth.%20Retailers%20are%20reporting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fstart-ups%2Fbeauty-retailers-report-high-demand-for-prestige-and-premium-segments-124022901044_1.html%5C%22%3Esales%20growth%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2018%25%20to%2050%25.%20The%20auto%20industry%2C%20too%2C%20reported%20that%20premium%20cars%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Fpost-pandemic-inequality-surge-in-premium-car-sales-lower-price-segment-stalls-8211026%2F%5C%22%3Ewere%20selling%20faster%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20low-priced%20ones.%20These%20again%20point%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20pyramid%20being%20able%20to%20buy%20more%20luxury%20goods%2C%20while%20the%20common%20man%20still%20finds%20it%20very%20difficult%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20private%20consumption%20forms%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20overall%20economic%20demand%2C%20and%20if%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20grow%20fast%20across%20the%20board%2C%20eventually%20high%20investment%20levels%20could%20end%20up%20in%20unproductive%20surplus%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%20gross%20capital%20formation%20in%20the%20quarter%20grew%20at%2011%25%2C%20led%20by%20government%20investment.%20However%2C%20private%20investment%20still%20continues%20to%20struggle.%20According%20to%20CMIE%2C%20new%20investment%20proposal%20levels%20from%20the%20private%20sector%20have%20remained%20lower%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20compared%20to%20the%20preceding%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20all%20this%20tell%20us%20about%20the%20better-than-expected%20GDP%20growth%20statistics%20and%20the%20real%20status%20of%20our%20economy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMake%20no%20mistake%2C%20rapid%20growth%20is%20necessary%20in%20an%20emerging%20economy%20like%20ours%20for%20us%20to%20take%20the%20steps%20towards%20a%20developed%20country.%20It%20gives%20us%20the%20wherewithal%20to%20invest%20in%20health%2C%20education%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20research%20and%20development%2C%20quality-competitiveness%2C%20sustainability%20etc.%20However%2C%20our%20current%20growth%20numbers%20don%E2%80%99t%20seem%20sufficient%20for%20us%20to%20achieve%20these%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistory%20suggests%20that%20the%20region%20now%20primarily%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%9D%20was%20among%20the%20wealthiest%20in%20the%20world%20in%20ancient%20times%2C%20surpassing%20many%20contemporary%20developed%20regions.%20However%2C%20despite%20this%20wealth%2C%20much%20of%20the%20population%20lived%20in%20poverty%2C%20particularly%20the%20lower%20castes%20and%20tribal%20communities%20who%20were%20marginalised%20from%20prosperity.%20Education%20was%20accessible%20to%20only%20a%20privileged%20few.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20region%20lagged%20behind%20in%20adopting%20technological%20advancements%20that%20could%20have%20enhanced%20productivity%20and%20quality%20of%20life%20for%20its%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20rulers%2C%20such%20as%20the%20rajas%20and%20nizams%2C%20enjoyed%20lives%20of%20opulence%20that%20were%20unparalleled%20in%20comparison%20to%20much%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast-forward%20to%20today.%20We%20need%20to%20ask%20whether%20economic%20growth%20is%20benefitting%20all%20sections%20of%20the%20population%20equally.%20Or%20are%20we%20again%20seeing%20a%20growing%20distance%20between%20the%20corporates%20(maharajas)%20and%20the%20common%20man%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2020th%20century%2C%20economics%20focused%20on%20the%20GDP%20growth%20statistics%20were%20a%20key%20indicator%20of%20economic%20health%2C%20alongside%20inflation.%20Hence%2C%20these%20statistics%20we