0his%20parents%20twice%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20February%2015%20%E2%80%93%20first%20noting%20that%20he%20would%20be%20done%20with%20his%20project%20soon%20and%20then%20to%20express%20concern%20about%20his%20research%20project.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COn%20my%20advice%2C%20Varad%20contacted%20Professor%20Singh.%20However%2C%20his%20response%20was%20unexpectedly%20harsh.%20After%20that%20Varad%20came%20back%20to%20the%20hostel%20room%20and%20he%20committed%20suicide.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHad%20it%20not%20been%20for%20Mr.%20Harpal%E2%80%99s%20hurtful%20remarks%2C%20our%20brilliant%20son%20would%20not%20have%20taken%20such%20a%20step%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20alleged%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVarad%20hailed%20from%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Nashik%20district.%20He%20had%20been%20selected%20for%20a%20job%20and%20was%20going%20to%20join%20the%20company%20in%20June.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20student%2C%20currently%20enrolled%20at%20IIT%20Delhi%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20heavy%20workload%20in%20laboratories%2C%20pressure%20to%20maintain%20high%20grades%2C%20and%20insufficient%20mental%20health%20support%2C%20particularly%20for%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20are%20significant%20contributors%20to%20the%20problem%20among%20IIT%20students.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20student%20added%20that%20those%20perceived%20as%20belonging%20to%20specific%20communities%2C%20such%20as%20SC%2FST%20or%20OBC%2C%20often%20experience%20caste%20discrimination%20from%20both%20fellow%20students%20and%20professors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20July%20last%20year%2C%20Ayush%20Ashna%2C%20a%20final-year%20student%20of%20B.%20Tech%20had%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%20IIT%20Delhi.%20Even%20at%20that%20time%2C%20student%20organisations%20had%20called%20his%20death%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmurder%E2%80%9D%20and%20demanded%20a%20thorough%20investig