f.%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20run%20the%20risk%20of%20conveying%20the%20wrong%20impression%20of%20his%20views%20through%20a%20precis%20or%20paraphrase.%20He%20has%20been%20courageous%20and%20outspoken%2C%20no%20doubt%20at%20considerable%20cost%20to%20himself%2C%20and%20I%20do%20not%20want%20to%20even%20inadvertently%20add%20to%20his%20problems%20by%20conveying%20the%20wrong%20impression%20of%20his%20position.%20So%20please%20watch%20this%20interview%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20will%20give%20you%20the%20list%20of%20questions%20asked%20which%20were%20followed%20meticulously.%20They%20will%20indicate%20the%20issues%20raised%20and%20help%20you%20understand%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20questions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20The%20Manipur%20Assembly%20has%20passed%20a%20resolution%20calling%20upon%20the%20central%20government%20%E2%80%9Cto%20completely%20abrogate%20the%20SoO%20pact%20with%20all%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20militant%20groups%E2%80%9D.%20It%20wants%20this%20done%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20interest%20of%20ensuring%20peace%20and%20security%20in%20the%20region%E2%80%9D.%20As%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Assembly%20and%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BJP%20how%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20In%20his%20message%20on%20X%20Chief%20Minister%20Biren%20Singh%20claimed%20the%20resolution%20was%20passed%20%E2%80%9Cunanimously%E2%80%9D.%20But%20if%20all%20ten%20Kuki-Zo%20MLAs%20were%20not%20present%20in%20the%20Assembly%20is%20he%20correct%20to%20call%20it%20unanimous%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20How%20did%20the%20ten%20Naga%20MLAs%20vote%3F%20I%20presume%20they%20were%20present%20and%20voted%20in%20favour.%20Am%20I%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20differences%20between%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20and%20the%20Nagas%20emerging%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4)%20Now%20in%20a%20press%20release%20that%20the%20ten%20Kuki%20MLAs%20issued%20you%20pointed%20out%20that%20a%20Joint%20Monitoring%20Group%20exists%20to%20oversee%20the%20agreement.%20In%20your%20press%20release%20you%20asked%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20like%20to%20question%20whether%20the%20resolution%20adopted%20by%20the%20august%20House%20was%20passed%20on%20any%20report%20or%20observations%20of%20the%20JMG%2C%20which%20is%20the%20only%20official%20mechanism%20to%20determine%20whether%20any%20violation%20of%20the%20ground%20rules%20has%20taken%20place%20or%20not.%E2%80%9D%20What%E2%80%99s%20your%20answer%20to%20that%20question%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5)%20Days%20after%20this%20resolution%20calling%20for%20the%20abrogation%20of%20the%20SoO%20agreement%2C%20the%20Manipur%20Assembly%20reaffirmed%20an%20earlier%20resolution%20of%202022%20calling%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20in%20Manipur.%20How%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6)%20In%20his%20message%20on%20X%20this%20is%20what%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CNRC%20is%20crucial%20for%20safeguarding%20the%20interests%20of%20our%20state%20and%20contributing%20to%20the%20greater%20good%20of%20our%20nation.%E2%80%9D%20He%E2%80%99s%20your%20party%20leader.%20How%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7)%20The%20paradox%20is%20whilst%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20is%20pushing%20to%20scrap%20the%20SoO%20agreements%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20allowing%20the%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20to%20become%20a%20law%20unto%20themselves%20and%20defy%20the%20police.%20A%20recent%20statement%20by%20the%20police%20accuses%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmany%20anti-social%20activities%20such%20as%20assaulting%20civilians%20and%20snatching%20vehicles%E2%80%9D.%20The%20police%20also%20say%20they%20are%20%E2%80%9Cinvolved%20in%20extortion%E2%80%9D.%20Last%20month%20the%20Tenggol%20abducted%20an%20Additional%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20because%20its%20Sekmai%20unit%20Chief%20was%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20snatching%20a%20vehicle%20from%20a%20petrol%20pump.%20How%20do%20you%20respond%20to%20all%20of%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8)%20The%20police%20have%20told%20The%20Hindu%20that%20%E2%80%9Cour%20hands%20are%20tied.%20We%20are%20stopped%20from%20taking%20action%20against%20the%20miscreants.%E2%80%9D%20Why%20is%20your%20Chief%20Minister%20not%20acting%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9)%20A%20second%20worrying%20development%20concerns%20the%20United%20National%20Liberation%20Front.%20After%20they%20signed%20a%20peace%20agreement%20in%20November%2C%20it%20was%20intended%20they%20would%20be%20kept%20in%20camps%20and%20monitored%20by%20central%20agencies.%20But%20The%20Hindu%20says%20they%20are%20roaming%20around%20in%20vehicles%2C%20brandishing%20weapons%2C%20indulging%20in%20violence%20against%20security%20forces%20and%20looting%20police%20armouries.%20Once%20again%2C%20why%20has%20your%20Chief%20Minister%20not%20done%20anything%20to%20stop%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10)%20It%20seems%20as%20if%20Biren%20Singh%20has%20two%20aims%20%E2%80%93%20to%20scupper%20the%20SoO%20agreement%2C%20which%20would%20upset%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%2C%20and%20give%20a%20free%20hand%20to%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20UNLF%2C%20which%20would%20please%20the%20Meitei%20community.%20Am%20I%20mistaken%20or%20am%20I%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E11)%20Let%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20you%20before%20we%20end.%20You%20have%20sharp%20differences%20with%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20your%20Meitei%20colleagues%20in%20the%20BJP.%20Why%20have%20you%20not%20resigned%20from%20the%20BJP%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E12)%20Have%20you%20raised%20your%20concerns%20directly%20with%20Amit%20Shah%3F%20And%20if%20you%20have%2C%20what%E2%80%99s%20the%20answer%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709704773000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F06111311%2FKT-6-March-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-arambai-tenggol-is-biren-singhs-creation-to-threaten-centre-today-its-more-important-than-govt%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20to%2