xtracted%20from%20mobile%20phones%20and%20laptops.%20However%2C%20our%20market%20research%20suggests%20that%20the%20organised%20sector%20will%20soon%20overtake%20the%20unorganised%20sector%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20sourcing%20these%20used%20batteries.%20Unlike%20laptop%20or%20phone%20batteries%2C%20EV%20batteries%20cannot%20be%20left%20in%20the%20unorganised%20sector.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20capacity%20or%20capability%20to%20handle%20them.%20One%20tonne%20of%20Li-ion%20battery%20waste%20is%20equivalent%20to%201%20e-bus%20battery%3B%203%20EV%20car%20batteries%3B%2029%20three-wheeler%20batteries%3B%2040%20two-wheeler%20batteries%3B%20or%2022%2C000%20mobile%20phone%20batteries%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Vikrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20sourced%2C%20you%20have%20to%20organise%20safe%20transportation%20of%20these%20old%20Li-ion%20batteries.%20We%20pay%20close%20attention%20to%20the%20packaging%20of%20the%20battery%20pack%2C%20discharging%20the%20battery%20at%20the%20collection%20point%2C%20ensuring%20no%20wiring%20is%20kept%20open%20or%20exposed%20and%20all%20the%20charging%20and%20discharging%20slots%20are%20well-capped.%20We%20have%20made%20sure%20to%20follow%20these%20basic%20safety%20measures%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Utkarsh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20startup%20is%20based%20out%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310909%2Fkarma-lakelands-gurugram-ashwani-khurana-sustainable-tourism-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGurugram%2C%20Haryana%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20its%20main%20recycling%20facility%20lies%20in%20Sikandrabad%20near%20Bulandshahr%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20There%20are%20two%20things%20that%20happen%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Facility-1709299273.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Why%20should%20you%20recycle%20Lithium-ion%20batteries%3F%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Facility-1709299273.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Facility-1709299273-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Facility-1709299273-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Facility-1709299273-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Facility-1709299273-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343656%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EStartup%E2%80%99s%20main%20chemical%20recycling%20facility%20where%20they%20deal%20with%20used%20Lithium-ion%20batteries%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20these%20used%20batteries%20reach%20the%20BatX%20facility%2C%20they%20will%20break%20them%20down%20into%20different%20modules%20and%20cells%2C%20run%20them%20through%20a%20series%20of%20tests%2C%20and%20conduct%20an%20analysis%20of%20the%20cell%20performance.%20If%20some%20of%20these%20cells%20still%20have%20some%20charge%20left%20and%20can%20perform%20for%20another%20life%20in%20a%20different%20application%2C%20the%20BatX%20team%20repurposes%20them%20for%20second-life%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20you%20have%20a%20cell%2C%20which%20can%20be%20reused%20for%20a%20torch%20or%20in%20a%20small%20electronic%20device.%20If%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20four-wheeler%20battery%2C%20we%20can%20reuse%20its%20cells%20in%20an%20energy%20storage%20application.%20We%20closely%20gauge%20how%20much%20charge%20remains%20in%20this%20battery.%20Using%20our%20IoT%20devices%2C%20we%20need%20to%20be%20very%20sure%20when%20the%20battery%20is%20coming%20to%20the%20end%20of%20its%20second%20life.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20important%20part%20of%20the%20process.%20If%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20malfunction%2C%20we%20repair%20it.%20Once%20those%20cells%20have%20been%20exhausted%2C%20however%2C%20we%20take%20them%20for%20recycling.%20If%20these%20cells%20cannot%20be%20reused%20as%20per%20our%20first%20assessment%2C%20we%20take%20them%20straight%20away%20for%20recycling.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20you%20create%20a%20circular%20economy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20second-life%20EV%20batteries%2C%20for%20example%2C%20BatX%20Energies%20has%20built%20100%25%20off-grid%20solar%20EV%20chargers%20for%20EV%20OEMs%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306265%2Fengineer-covers-long-distance-journey-in-electric-vehicle-sushil-reddy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMG%20Motor%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20have%20even%20developed%20home%20inverters%20employing%20second-life%20EV%20batteries%20at%20the%20same%20cost%20as%20a%20lead-acid%20inverter%2C%20which%20is%20hazardous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20developed%20a%20small%20unit%20which%20can%20run%20for%20five%20years.%20We%20are%20going%20to%20deploy%20these%20inverters%20soon%20in%20rural%20Rajasthan%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Once%20these%20second-life%20batteries%20come%20to%20the%20end%20of%20their%20lives%2C%20we%20will%20take%20them%20back%20and%20recycle%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Utkarsh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Operations-2-1709299355.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There's%20a%20lot%20of%20value%20in%20recycling%20in%20Lithium-ion%20batteries%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Operations-2-1709299355.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Operations-2-1709299355-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Operations-2-1709299355-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Operations-2-1709299355-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Operations-2-1709299355-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343658%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWorking%20at%20the%20BatX%20Energies%20facility%20where%20they%20recycle%20used%20Lithium-ion%20batteries%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20batteries%20are%20deemed%20not%20fit%20for%20second-life%20applications%2C%20they%20are%20dismantled%2C%20discharged%2C%20and%20crushed%20into%20powder%20at%20their%20facility%20in%20Sikandrabad%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20They%20call%20this%20crushed%20powder%20%E2%80%98black%20mass%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20then%20transported%20to%20their%20main%20chemical%20recycling%20facility%2C%20and%20here%2C%20they%20extract%20materials%20like%20lithium%2C%20cobalt%2C%20nickel%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20black%20mass%2C%20all%20battery%20grade%20material%20including%20graphite%20is%20removed%2C%20and%20then%20impurities%20like%20aluminium%2C%20copper%20and%20cake.%20After%20this%2C%20we%20extract%20lithium%2C%20nickel%20and%20cobalt.%20Once%20we%20extract%20these%20materials%2C%20we%20sell%20them%20to%20material%20refiners%20who%20use%20them%20to%20make%20new%20Li-ion%20cells.%20But%20materials%20like%20lithium%20are%20also%20used%20in%20the%20pharmaceutical%20industry%20to%20make%20anti-depression%20medication%2C%20etc.%20Cobalt%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20used%20in%20the%20ceramic%20and%20pain%20industry%20while%20Nickel%20is%20employed%20in%20electroplating%20and%20the%20fertiliser%20industry%20as%20well.%20We%20only%20produce%20high-grade%20material%20(99.6%25%20purity)%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Utkarsh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikrant%20goes%20on%20to%20claim%20that%20the%20process%20they%20have%20developed%20to%20repurpose%20or%20recycle%20these%20old%20batteries%20is%20chemistry-agnostic%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20they%20are%20lithium%20iron%20phosphate%20(LFP)%20batteries%2C%20lithium%20nickel%20manganese%20cobalt%20(NMC)%20batteries%2C%20Li-ion%20batteries%2C%20or%20lead%20acid%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20us%20five%20years%20to%20design%20and%20develop%20this%20process%20we%20have%20established.%20We%20currently%20have%20a%20patent%20on%20our%20%E2%80%98Waste%20to%20Zero%20Emission%20Technology%E2%80%99.%20The%20patent%20is%20on%20their%20apparatus%2C%20methods%20and%20process.%20Since%20we%20initially%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20funds%2C%20we%20developed%20the%20recycling%20plant%20ourselves.%20We%20have%20not%20imported%20any%20of%20the%20machinery%20in%20our%20production%20plant%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Vikrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20near%20future%2C%20however%2C%20BatX%20will%20look%20to%20alter%20their%20operations%20based%20on%20a%20hub%20and%20spoke%20model.%20Although%20their%20main%20centre%20of%20operations%20lies%20in%20Sikandrabad%2C%20UP%20(Hub)%2C%20they%20are%20planning%20to%20set%20up%20different%20facilities%20(spokes)%20in%20places%20like%20Hosur%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Siliguri%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20and%20Gujarat.%20Why%20are%20they%20adopting%20this%20new%20operating%20model%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20say%2C%20we%20collect%20old%20Li-ion%20batteries%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336276%2Fmadhura-rajvanshi-fulbright-scholar-distinguished-award-phaltan-rural-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMaharashtra%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebut%20want%20to%20transport%20them%20to%20our%20hub%20in%20UP.%20Despite%20all%20the%20safety%20measures%20we%20take%2C%20there%20is%20some%20risk%20involved%20in%20transporting%20them.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20are%20planning%20to%20create%20facilities%20(spokes)%20in%20states%20like%20Gujarat%20(and%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Karnataka)%20so%20that%20we%20can%20transport%20our%20old%20batteries%20from%20Maharashtra%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-5-1709299437.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Extracting%20key%20materials%20while%20recycling%20Lithium-ion%20batteries%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-5-1709299437.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-5-1709299437-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-5-1709299437-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-5-1709299437-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-5-1709299437-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343660%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EExtracting%20key%20materials%20while%20recycling%20Lithium-ion%20batteries%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFunding%20and%20looking%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20December%202023%2C%20BatX%20Energies%20raised%20USD%205%20million%20in%20pre-Series%20A%20funding.%20The%20round%20was%20led%20by%20investors%2C%20such%20as%20Zephyr%20Peacock%2C%20but%20also%20s