ebetterindia.com%2F343547%2Fisro-iirs-free-online-course-remote-sensing-tech-applications-eligibility-criteria-apply-now%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Brilliant%20Initiative%20Helps%20Blind%20Children%20Appreciate%20Art%20%26amp%3B%20Heritage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20sponsored%20by%20Asian%20Paints%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20group%20of%20students%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20a%20seven-foot%20wall%20inside%20the%20prayer%20hall%20at%20the%20Rajasthan%20Netraheen%20Kalyan%20Sangh%20School%20in%20Jaipur.%20There%20is%20an%20undeniable%20enthusiasm%20among%20them%20as%20they%20discuss%20the%20artwork%20sprawled%20out%20on%20it.%20The%20room%2C%20which%20was%20once%20only%20a%20place%20for%20assemblies%2C%20has%20now%20taken%20on%20a%20new%20avatar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20the%20students%20appear%20to%20be%20marvelling%20at%20what%20they%20see.%20But%20a%20closer%20look%20will%20reveal%20they%20are%20blind.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337583%2Ftulsi-village-chhattisgarh-youtube-village-hummer-studios-being-chhattisgarhiya-alwa-jalwa-gold-cg04%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20art%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20front%20of%20them%20must%20thus%20assume%20a%20%E2%80%98tactile%E2%80%99%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20suffices%20to%20say%20that%20the%20art%20is%20novel%20in%20its%20creation.%20For%20one%2C%20it%20beckons%20the%20students%20to%20touch%20it%20to%20understand%20it%2C%20thus%20disrupting%20the%20traditional%20notion%20that%20art%20needs%20to%20be%20appreciated%20from%20a%20distance.%20For%20another%2C%20it%20acts%20as%20a%20medium%20for%20the%20children%20to%20delve%20deeper%20into%20the%20culture%20of%20their%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBringing%20this%20to%20fruition%20is%20a%20project%20%E2%80%98Sparsh%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20initiative%20launched%20by%20Asian%2